2F%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmahua-moitra-cash-for-query-hiranandani-parliament-interview-9003140%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eoutlets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20addressed%20the%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20her%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20was%20no%20quid%20pro%20quo%20between%20her%20and%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20admitted%20that%20she%20had%20given%20her%20Parliament%20login%20ID%20and%20password%20to%20the%20businessman%2C%20to%20have%20someone%20in%20his%20office%20to%20type%20in%20the%20questions%20to%20be%20asked%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20She%20said%20the%20process%20requires%20a%20One-Time%20Password%20(OTP)%2C%20and%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20someone%20else%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20Hiranandani%2C%20logged%20into%20her%20account%20and%20posted%20questions%20on%20her%20behalf%20is%20%E2%80%98ludicrous%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20enter%20Parliament%2C%20there%20are%20no%20NIC%20%5BNational%20Informatics%20Centre%5D%20rules%20for%20Parliament.%20No%20MP%20does%20their%20own%20questions%20%E2%80%93%20LAMPs%20(Legislative%20Assistants%20to%20Members%20of%20Parliament)%20do%20it%2C%20or%20interns%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmahua-moitra-cash-for-query-hiranandani-parliament-interview-9003140%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20and%20answer%20password%20does%20not%20give%20you%20access%20to%20the%20vaults%20of%20the%20RBI%20or%20the%20Budget%20document%2C%20it%20is%20just%20to%20upload%20or%20update%20your%20question.%20An%20OTP%20comes%20to%20your%20mobile%2C%20and%20in%2099%25%20of%20the%20cases%2C%20MPs%20do%20not%20give%20their%20phone%20numbers%20for%20the%20OTP.%20But%20in%20my%20case%2C%20my%20phone%20number%20is%20given%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20became%20an%20MP%20and%20since%20I%20represent%20a%20remote%20constituency%20(Krishnanagar)%2C%20I%20asked%20Darshan%20to%20get%20someone%20in%20his%20office%20to%20type%20down%20the%20question%20and%20upload%20it.%20He%20is%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20do%20not%20think%20there%20is%20anything%20wrong%20with%20it.%20How%20do%20you%20know%20which%20business%20group%20goes%20and%20gives%20questions%20to%20your%20intern%20or%20LAMP%20to%20file%3F%E2%80%A6%20I%20have%20given%20him%20the%20password%20and%20login%20for%20someone%20in%20his%20office%20to%20type%20it%20down%20and%20upload.%20Since%20the%20OTP%20comes%20to%20me%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20Darshan%20or%20anyone%20putting%20it%20without%20my%20knowledge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%E2%80%98cash-for-query%E2%80%99%20allegation%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20approached%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20TMC%20leader%20had%20accepted%20bribes%20and%20favours%20in%20return%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20businessman%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20responded%20to%20this%20allegation%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CTell%20me%2C%20where%20is%20the%20money%3F%20The%20main%20thing%20to%20prove%20is%20the%20quid%20pro%20quo.%20Darshan%20is%20an%20Indian%20citizen%2C%20he%20runs%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20IT%20firms%20in%20the%20country%20and%20its%20biggest%20client%20is%20the%20GOI%20(Government%20of%20India).%20So%20he%20cannot%20be%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99.%20One%20of%20his%20secretaries%20typed%20the%20questions%20I%20framed%E2%80%A6%20Darshan%20in%20his%20affidavit%20(to%20the%20Ethics%20Committee)%20says%20that%20he%20is%20the%20biggest%20fan%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20Where%20did%20he%20attack%20Adani%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20analysis%20given%20in%20the%20affidavit%20(by%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai)%20of%20my%20questions%20is%20laughable.%20To%20my%20question%20as%20to%20the%20statistics%20regarding%20the%20quality%20of%20service%20provided%20by%20telecom%20companies%2C%20Dehadrai%20has%20written%20as%20analysis%20that%2C%20just%20a%20day%20earlier%2C%20Hiranandani%20had%20hired%20a%20former%20Reliance%20Jio%20executive.%20What%20rubbish%20is%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20Adani%20has%20used%20the%20government%2C%20ED%20(Enforcement%20Directorate)%20and%20CBI%20to%20shut%20up%20competitors.%20I%20am%20fully%20within%20my%20rights%20to%20raise%20questions%20against%20Adani%E2%80%A6%20What%20you%20need%20to%20prove%20is%20that%20I%20took%20cash%20for%20this.%20Where%20is%20the%20cash%3F%E2%80%A6%20What%20is%20the%20secret%20answer%20I%20am%20getting%20on%20Adani%20that%20Hiranandani%20could%20not%20get%20on%20his%20own%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fcash-for-query-claim-mahua-moitra-exclusive-interview-nishikant-dubey-ethics-committee-2454701-2023-10-27%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20the%20cash-for-query%20has%20fallen%20flat%2C%20this%20is%20being%20made%20out%20to%20be%20some%20great%20issue%20of%20national%20security.%20Mr.%20Dubey%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20press%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20national%20security%20issue.%20The%20NIC%20login%20has%20no%20rules%20as%20to%20who%20can%20have%20your%20login.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-modi-government-and-adani-train-guns-on-opposition-mp-mahua-moitra-heres-what-we-know-and-dont-know%5C%22%3EAs%20Modi%20Government%20and%20Adani%20Train%20Guns%20on%20Opposition%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20We