%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Quick%20Start%20program%20class%3Cp%3EJacob%20Zinkula%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EQuick%20Start%20student%20Collin%20Gardner%2C%2022%2C%20told%20Insider%20he%20learned%20about%20the%20opportunity%20from%20a%20YouTube%20ad.%20He%20had%20been%20working%20at%20Taco%20Bell%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20and%20after%20earning%20his%20bachelor's%20in%20psychology%20in%20May%2C%20he%20said%20he%20struggled%20to%20find%20a%20job%20in%20the%20field%20because%20most%20required%20a%20Master's%20degree.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20applied%20because%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20simple%2C%20inexpensive%20certification%20that%20would%20get%20me%20a%20job%20somewhat%20immediately%20working%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20hoping%20that%20I%20would%20enjoy%20the%20work%20and%20get%20at%20least%20better%20pay%20than%20Taco%20Bell%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Rojas%2C%20who%20works%20in%20the%20telecommunications%20industry%2C%20said%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20pursue%20a%20technician%20job%2C%20but%20wants%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20potential%20opportunities%20the%20industry%20might%20provide%20someday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20take%20this%20course%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20industry%20since%20new%20manufacturing%20plants%20and%20new%20jobs%20are%20coming%20to%20Arizona%2C%26quot%3B%20Rojas%2C%2038%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20also%20just%20enjoy%20learning%20about%20new%20things%2C%20and%20this%20is%20cool%20and%20interesting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20October%2C%2065%25%20of%20Quick%20Start%20students%20have%20been%20people%20of%20color%2C%2032%25%20have%20been%20women%2C%2044%25%20have%20been%20between%2018%20and%2029%20years%20old%2C%20and%2050%25%20have%20been%20first-generation%20college%20students%2C%20according%20to%20program%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuick%20Start%20provides%20courses%20at%20different%20times%20of%20the%20day%20to%20accommodate%20individuals%20who%20work%20full-time%20%E2%80%94%20mine%20was%20scheduled%20from%204%3A30%20p.m.%20to%208%3A30%20p.m.%20each%20day.%20The%20class%20included%20about%2010%20students%20and%20a%20professor%2C%20Dan%20Dangelo%2C%20who%20also%20works%20as%20an%20engineer%20at%20Intel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20a%20%2415%20registration%20fee%2C%20the%20tuition%20for%20the%20course%20is%20%24291.%20However%20the%20tuition%20isn't%20paid%20up%20front%2C%20and%20any%20Arizona%20resident%20who%20successfully%20passes%20the%20course%20has%20their%20tuition%20fully%20covered%20by%20grant%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EClasses%20were%20a%20mixture%20of%20lectures%20and%20labs%20%E2%80%94%20with%20%E2%80%9Cbunny%20suits%E2%80%9D%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quick%20Start%20students%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a86c10487ff031caf4170%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuick%20Start%20students%3Cp%3EJacob%20Zinkula%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20start%20of%20classes%2C%20students%20were%20shown%20videos%20to%20help%20introduce%20them%20to%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20classes%20included%20a%20mix%20of%20lectures%20and%20labs.%20For%20one%20lab%20assignment%2C%20students%20put%20on%20%26quot%3Bbunny%20suits%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20garments%20used%20to%20minimize%20contaminants%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20and%20practiced%20troubleshooting%20equipment%20with%20various%20tools%20in%20a%20simulation%20chip%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20bunny%20suits%20might%20look%20fun%20to%20wear%2C%20they%20can%20get%20hot%20and%20uncomfortable%2C%20particularly%20for%20industry%20workers%20who%20don%20them%20for%20hours%20at%20a%20time.%20A%20program%20representative%20told%20me%20the%20suit%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20reasons%20some%20students%20ultimately%20decide%20the%20industry%20isn't%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20two%20weeks%2C%20the%20students%20are%20introduced%20to%20topics%20that%20include%20electrical%20theory%2C%20circuits%2C%20schematics%2C%20hand%20tools%2C%20safety%2C%20clean%20room%20protocols%2C%20model-based%20problem%20solving%2C%20lean%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20vacuum%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20course%20material%20might%20seem%20quite%20complicated%2C%2093%25%20of%20students%20who%20completed%20the%20full%20course%20as%20of%20June%20passed%20the%20final%20exam%2C%20according%20to%20program%20data.%20These%20students%20received%20a%20semiconductor%20pre-apprentice%20credential%2C%20which%20some%20have%20used%20to%20land%20a%20job%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EStudents%20have%20had%20mixed%20success%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20finding%20a%20career%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Quick%20Start%20lab%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65395d2096f7540cd065a6a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuick%20Start%20students%20work%20on%20a%20lab%20assignment%20in%20September%3Cp%3EJacob%20Zinkula%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20classes%2C%20the%20professor%20regularly%20advised%20students%20to%20remember%20certain%20pieces%20of%20information%20for%20any%20future%20interviews.%20Quick%20Start%20students%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finfo.maricopacorporate.com%2Fsemiconductor%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eare%20promised%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20opportunity%20to%20interview%20with%20semiconductor%20companies%20through%20the%20program's%20occasional%20job%20fairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20240%20former%20Quick%20Start%20students%20who%20filled%20out%20an%20employment%20outcome%20form%20as%20of%20June%2C%2031%25%20said%20they%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bhired%20in%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20program%20data.%20Fifty-eight%20percent%20were%20still%20looking%20for%20employment%2C%20and%208%25%20were%20not%20looking%20for%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20several%20years%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-tech-war-computer-chips-semiconductor-plants-costing-americans-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esemiconductor%20jobs%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20expected%20to%20hit%20Arizona%20and%20provide%20additional%20pathways%20for%20Quick%20Start%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F6973aa75-0e25-49b8-b59d-5e8d38faa6b2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eslowdown%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20demand%20for%20chips%20has%20led%20some%20companies%20in%20the%20industry%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dice.com%2Fcareer-advice%2Fqualcomm-layoffs-reflect-interesting-moment-for-chip-industry%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elay%20off%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20enact%20hiring%20freezes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeah%20Palmer%2C%20executive%20director%20for%20the%20Arizona%20Advanced%20Manufacturing%20Institute%20at%20Mesa%20Community%20College%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20this%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20many%20Quick%20Start%20graduates%20to%20find%20employment%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20slow%20down%20our%20pipeline%20so%20that%20we're%20not%20putting%20out%20more%20people%20with%20absolutely%20no%20possibility%20of%20employment%2C%26quot%3B%20Palmer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20after%20Gardner's%20Quick%20Start%20class%20ended%2C%20Insider%20followed%20up%20with%20him%20to%20learn%20what%20his%20plan%20was%20moving%20forward.%20He's%20grown%20more%20pessimistic%20about%20his%20chances%20of%20landing%20a%20job%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20keep%20looking%2C%20but%20it%20seems%