ow%2F104778845.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104778845.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20families%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%20held%20by%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20are%20extremely%20worried%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20their%20loved%20ones.%20The%20Hostages%20and%20Missing%20Families%20Forum%20stated%20that%20the%20hostages%20are%20being%20subjected%20to%20heavy%20bombardment%20and%20their%20families%20are%20anxious%20about%20the%20ground%20invasion%20putting%20them%20in%20more%20danger.%20Israel%20has%20been%20bombarding%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20since%20Hamas%20launched%20an%20assault%20in%20October.%20The%20air%20strikes%20and%20artillery%20fire%20have%20killed%20over%207%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Palestinian%20health%20officials.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fanxiety-racks-israeli-hostage-families-as-army-assaults-gaza%2Farticleshow%2F104778845.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fanxiety-racks-israeli-hostage-families-as-army-assaults-gaza%2Famp_articleshow%2F104778845.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fanxiety-racks-israeli-hostage-families-as-army-assaults-gaza%2Famp_articleshow%2F104778845.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20LinkedIn%20conversation%20turned%20into%20what%20I%20thought%20was%20a%20job%20interview.%20It%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20more%20like%20a%20date%20%E2%80%93%26nbsp%3Band%20left%20me%20feeling%20gross%20and%20dirty.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jenna%20Vaught%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6530edbb96f7540cd0602424%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJenna%20Vaught.%20%3Cp%3EJenna%20Vaught%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJenna%20Vaught%20was%20a%20college%20student%20using%20LinkedIn%20to%20get%20started%20with%20her%20career.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20what%20she%20thought%20was%20a%20job%20interview%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20country%20club%20lunch%20with%20an%20older%20man.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BHe%20knew%20he%20could%20do%20this.%20It%20just%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20a%20thing%20for%20him%20to%20play%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Jenna%20Vaught%20about%20her%20experience%20of%20being%20baited%20on%20LinkedIn.%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20LinkedIn%20messages%20with%20the%20man%20as%20well%20as%20the%20details%20he%20posted%20on%20the%20site.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%20I%20was%20a%20college%20junior%20at%20Florida%20Gulf%20Coast%20University.%20I%20had%20just%20one%20more%20year%20to%20go%20before%20graduating%20with%20a%20bachelor's%20in%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20also%20working%20full%20time%20at%20a%20restaurant%20called%20the%20Capital%20Grille.%20It%20was%20a%20real%20%26quot%3Bin%20spot%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%93%20I%20once%20met%20Judge%20Judy%20there.%20People%20who%20thought%20they%20were%20someone%20in%20Naples%2C%20Florida%20would%20go%20there%20and%20brag%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20graduation%20was%20coming%20up%20and%20I%20needed%20marketing%20experience.%20So%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20an%20internship%20to%20take%20that%20next%20career%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20LinkedIn%20back%20then.%20I%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20of%20my%20friends%20to%20start%20using%20it%20and%20had%20cracked%20the%20code.%20If%20you%20can%20connect%20with%20one%20person%20from%20a%20bigger%20company%20then%20you%20can%20just%20keep%20networking.%20I%20really%20liked%20it%20for%20that%20reason%20and%20used%20it%20all%20the%20time%20to%20message%20people%20with%20careers%20questions%20or%20things%20for%20school%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUp%20to%20that%20point%2C%20all%20my%20experiences%20had%20been%20good.%20And%20then%20I%20had%20the%20most%20bizarre%20lunch%20of%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20new%20connection%20on%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20December%202020%20when%20I%20was%20contacted%20by%20a%20wealth%20advisor%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20a%20regular%20at%20the%20Capital%20Grille%20and%20had%20spotted%20it%20on%20my%20profile.%20He%20asked%20if%20I%20could%20call%20him%20about%20an%20internship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221233%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jenna%20Vaught%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65327256be9edfa8eda5b068%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221646%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJenna%20worked%20at%20the%20Capital%20Grille%20in%20Naples%2C%20Florida%20while%20she%20studied.%20%3Cp%3EJenna%20Vaught%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20worked%20at%20Merrill%20Lynch%2C%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20personal%20marketing%20intern%20for%20financial%20conferences%20he%20ran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%2020%20at%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20literally%20saying%20yes%20to%20everything%20because%20I%20needed%20to%20land%20anything%20I%20could%20get%2C%20plus%20having%20Merrill%20Lynch%20on%20my%20resum%C3%A9%20would%20be%20a%20great%20step%20up.%20So%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Byeah%2C%20I'll%20give%20you%20a%20call.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20few%20phone%20calls%20and%20messaged%20back%20and%20forth%20about%20the%20job.%20But%20he%20also%20asked%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20if%20I%20could%20get%20him%20reservations%20at%20the%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20him%20up%20on%20the%20restaurant's%20system%20to%20check%20he%20was%20who%20he%20said%20he%20was.%20As%20far%20as%20I%20could%20tell%2C%20everything%20on%20his%20LinkedIn%20profile%2C%20his%20name%20and%20position%20at%20Merrill%20Lynch%2C%20was%20all%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHe%20set%20a%20date%20for%20the%20job%20interview%2C%20but%20something%20wasn't%20right%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20set%20a%20date%20and%20sent%20me%20a%20location.%20My%20generation%20doesn't%20really%20question%20things%20like%20that.%20We've%20been%20desensitized%20to%20meeting%20strangers%20on%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20I%20showed%20up%20it%20was%20at%20this%20posh%20country%20club%20on%20a%20lake%20in%20a%20gated%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20just%20immediately%20regretting%20my%20outfit%20choice.%20It%20was%20a%20resort%20hotel%20filled%20with%20women%20in%20glamorous%20sundresses%2C%20and%20I%20was%20there%20in%20my%20slacks%2C%20a%20blouse%2C%20and%20little%20flats.%20I%20felt%20very%20self-conscious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20must%20have%20been%20in%20his%20early%20forties%20and%20definitely%20had%20that%20frat%20boy%20personality.%20You%20can%20tell%20by%20the%20way%20some%20men%20carry%20themselves.%20They%20think%20they're%20the%20shit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20and%20he%20seemed%20to%20know%20everyone%20that%20worked%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22826%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jenna%20Vaught%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65327bc596908fd7cdb38273%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22943%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJenna%20Vaught.%20%3Cp%3EJenna%20Vaught%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20probably%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20way%20through%20the%20lunch%20when%20I%20was%20watching%20him%20check%20out%20all%20the%20female%20servers%2C%20that%20I%20realized%20he%20wasn't%20really%20there%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20all%20about%20him.%20I%20honestly%20can't%20even%20remember%20half%20of%20the%20conversations%20because%20my%20brain%20was%20flatlining%20from%20how%20uncomfortable%20it%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20leave%2C%20but%20part%20of%20me%20still%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20if%20this%20is%20legit%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20wasn't%20any%20physical%20hand-on-leg%20moments%2C%20but%20as%20a%20woman%2C%20the%20hairs%20on%20your%20neck%20stand%20up.%20I%20knew%20that%20something%20was%20weird%20about%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20didn't%20talk%20about%20the%20internship%20until%20the%20lunch%20was%20basically%20over%20and%20I%20brought%20it%20up.%20Still%20hoping%20to%20impress%20him%2C%20I%20gave%20over%20all%20my%20ideas%20on%20outreach%2C%20social%20media%20marketing%2C%20LinkedIn%20mailing%20lists%2C%20and%20pamphlets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20still%20a%20student%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20what%20I%20was%20talking%20about%20and%20it%20felt%20good%20that%20someone%20was%20asking%20me%20my%20opinion%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThat%20was%20the%20last%20I%20ever%20heard%20from%20him%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20lunch%2C%20I%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20be%20nice%2C%20so%20that%20it%20would%20be%20over%20sooner.%20I%20never%20heard%20from%20him%20again%20and%20he%20disconnected%20with%20me%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20back%20it%20seems%20like%20it%20was%20a%20power%20move.%20I%20was%20there%20and%20available%2C%20almost%20like%20a%20plaything.%20And%20he%20got%20my%20ideas%20for%20free.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20he%20ever%20used%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwenty-year-old%20me%20wanted%20to%20post%20about%20it%20on%20LinkedIn%20or%20even%20go%20to%20his%20employer%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20think%20I'd%20be%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20sent%20him%20a%20message%20saying%20that%20I%20felt%20disrespected.%20But%20as%20a%20college%20kid%20looking%20to%20start%20my%20professional%20life%20it%20was%20really%20discouraging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20lots%20of%20things%20that%20I%20questioned%20about%20why%20it%20didn't%20work%20out.%20Was%20it%20because%20I'm%20a%20woman%3F%20Was%20it%20because%20I'm%20young%3F%20Was%20I%20not%20attractive%20enough%20for%20this%20person%20to%20hire%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20kept%20making%20excuses%20for%20him%2C%20but%20now%20I%20realize%20this%20kind%20of%20experience%20just%20shouldn't%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%2021%20and%20he%20was%2015%20years%20older%20than%20me.%20We%20could%20have%20gone%20to%20a%20public%20place.%20But%20I%20was%20there%20and%20available%2C%20and%20he%20knew%20he%20could%20do%20this.%20It%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20a%20thing%20for%20him%20to%20play%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20no%20hatred%20towards%20men%2C%20but%20I%20just%20don't%20think%20that%20would%20happen%20to%20a%20man.%20And%20that's%20why%20it%20makes%20me%20feel%20gross%20and%20dirty%20and%20taken%20advantage%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENow%20I%20work%20for%20women%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20college%20LinkedIn%20was%20the%20only%20platform%20I%20could%20use%20to%20really%20find%20something%2C%20but%20now%20I%20can't%20rely%20on%20it%2C%20especially%20for%20networking.%20It's%20turned%20into%20just%20another%20Facebook.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jenna%20Vaught%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6532824896f7540cd0616604%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJenna%20now%20works%20for%20an%20all-female%20team%20at%20an%20ad%20agency.%3Cp%3EJenna%20Vaught%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20still%20have%20to%20rely%20on%20these%20third%20party%20websites%20to%20help%20you%20find%20a%20job%2C%20which%20holds%20the%20same%20risks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20value%20myself%20a%20lot%20more%20now%20than%20I%20did%20when%20I%20was%20younger%20and%20know%20that%20my%20time%20is%20also%20money.%20You%20shouldn't%20be%20exploited%20for%20being%20young%20and%20inexperienced.