s%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20just%20to%20focus%20for%20a%20moment%20on%20his%20manipulation%20of%20the%20sense%20of%20threat%20this%20is%20his%20hallmark.%20This%20is%20his%20most%20distinctive%20position%20to%20always%20exaggerate%20the%20existential%20threat%20to%20Israel%2C%20and%20for%20decades%20he%20has%20been%20saying%20that%20Iran%20poses%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20Israel.%20Well%2C%20Iran%20doesn%E2%80%99t%2C%20Israel%20has%20a%20monopoly%20of%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20and%20Israel%20threatens%20Iran.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20for%20this%20reason%20that%20the%20Iranians%20feel%20so%20strongly%20that%20they%20need%20to%20acquire%20nuclear%20weapons%20to%20counter%20the%20Israeli%20threat.%20So%2C%20Iran%20isn%E2%80%99t%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20Israel%2C%20and%20Netanyahu%20has%20been%20saying%20repeatedly%20that%20Hamas%20poses%20an%20existential%20threat%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20Hamas%20doesn%E2%80%99t%2C%20Hamas%20is%20a%20very%20small%20poorly%20equipped%20organisation%2C%20which%20poses%20no%20threat%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20basic%20security%2C%20which%20engages%20in%20terrorism%20in%20pinpricks.%20And%20terrorism%20is%20the%20weapon%20of%20the%20weak.%20Netanyahu%20is%20a%20great%20manipulator%2C%20and%20also%20Netanyahu%20has%20misled%20the%20Israeli%20public%20into%20thinking%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20are%20finished%2C%20that%20Israel%20has%20defeated%20them%2C%20they%20are%20defeated%20people.%20Israel%20has%20a%20free%20hand%20to%20do%20whatever%20it%20likes%20on%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20Israel%20has%20effectively%20sealed%20Gaza%20off%20and%20it%20ceased%20to%20be%20a%20problem.%20The%20attack%20on%20October%207%20meant%20the%20collapse%20of%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20dealing%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20third%20broad%20thematic%20point%20I%20want%20to%20take%20up%20is%20the%20one%20you%20mentioned%20earlier%20in%20an%20answer.%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20the%20West.%20But%20I%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20me%20to%20repeat%20it%20for%20the%20audience.%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20what%20you%E2%80%99ve%20written%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Western%20policy%20of%20refusing%20to%20engage%20with%20Hamas%2C%20of%20supporting%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20abuse%20of%20the%20right%20to%20self-defence%2C%20and%20of%20supplying%20it%20with%20weapons%20that%20are%20repeatedly%20used%20to%20bomb%20a%20defenceless%20people%2C%20is%20morally%20indefensible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20are%20you%20saying%20that%20the%20West%20bears%20much%20of%20the%20blame%20for%20the%20repeated%20failure%20to%20resolve%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20problem%3F%20And%20perhaps%20also%20for%20the%20trauma%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20have%20had%20to%20live%20through%20for%20at%20least%2056%20years%2C%20if%20not%20a%20lot%20longer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EProfessor%20Shlaim%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EIsrael%20bears%20the%20largest%20part%20of%20the%20responsibility%20for%20dispossessing%20and%20oppressing%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20The%20Israeli%20occupation%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%20is%20the%20most%20prolonged%20and%20brutal%20military%20occupation%20of%20modern%20times.%20But%20the%20West%20also%20bears%20a%20part%20of%20the%20responsibility%20for%20the%20present%20and%20past%2C%20because%20of%20its%20massive%20support%20for%20Israel%2C%20its%20supply%20of%20arms%20to%20Israel%2C%20and%20its%20diplomatic%20protection%20of%20Israel.%20Britain%20and%20America%20use%20the%20veto%20at%20the%20Security%20Council%20to%20defeat%20every%20resolution%20that%20is%20critical%20of%20Israel%2C%20and%20Britain%20and%20America%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20investigation%20by%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20of%20war%20crimes%20in%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20very%20revealing.%20There%20is%20an%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%2C%20and%20there%20is%20a%20case%20for%20investigating%20war%20crimes%20both%20by%20Hamas%20and%20by%20Israel%2C%20and%20yet%20both%20Britain%20and%20America%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20investigation%20of%20Israel%20in%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court.%20That%20means%20that%20they%20consider%20Israel%20to%20be%20above%20international%20law%20and%20above%20international%20scrutiny.%20This%20is%20why%20this%20unconditional%20character%2C%20this%20unconditional%20nature%20%5Bof%5D%20Western%20support%20for%20Israel%20is%20what%20accounts%20for%2C%20as%20I%20said%20earlier%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20Israel%20can%20act%20with%20impunity%2C%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20Israel%20until%20now%20has%20been%20able%20to%20get%20away%2C%20literally%2C%20with%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20committing%20murder%20on%20a%20massive%20scale%20every%20day%20in%20Gaza%2C%20but%20I%20have%20one%20glimmer%20of%20hope%20about%20the%20future%2C%20and%20that%20is%20that%20there%20is%20a%20complete%20disconnect%20between%20the%20Western%20government%20and%20the%20people%20of%20these%20Western%20countries.%20The%20governments%20are%20blindly%2C%20uncritically%20supportive%20of%20Israel%20whatever%20it%20does%2C%20but%20the%20people%20in%20America%2C%20and%20in%20Europe%2C%20and%20Britain%2C%20are%20increasingly%20and%20overwhelmingly%20pro-Palestinian.%20I%20hope%20that%20eventually%2C%20Western%20foreign%20policy%20will%20catch%20up%20with%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20in%20the%20street.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20me%20pick%20up%20briefly%2C%20Professor%20Shlaim%2C%20on%20something%20you%20said%20in%20that%20answer%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ve%20also%20written%20about%20it%20in%20a%20piece%20as%20recently%20as%20May%202019.%20That%20piece%20ends%20with%20the%20following%20sentence%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20you%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20specific%20duty%20of%20the%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20to%20hold%20Israel%20to%20account%20for%20the%20war%20crimes%20it%20committed%20in%20the%20past%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20ongoing%20assault%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20someone%20who%20served%20proudly%20and%20loyally%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Army%20in%20the%20mid-1960s%2C%20do%20you%20really%20mean%20that%20about%20your%20own%20country%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EProfessor%20Shlaim%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EI%20served%20proudly%20and%20loyally%20in%20the%20IDF%20(Israeli%20Defence%20Forces)%20in%20the%20mid-1960s%20because%20at%20that%20time%20the%20IDF%20was%20true%20to%20its%20name.%20It%20was%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%2C%20it%20was%20a%20regular%20army%20that%20was%20there%20to%20defend%20the%20country%20against%20attack%20from%20the%20regular%20armies%20of%20the%20surrounding%20Arab%20states.%20Everything%20changed%20in%20June%201967.%20Israel%20travelled%20its%20territory%2C%20it%20occupied%20territory%20from%20all%20its%20neighbours%2C%20and%20my%20little%20army%20was%20changed%20and%20Israel%20became%20a%20brutal%20colonial%20power%20oppressing%20millions%20of%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20occupied%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20IDF%20was%20transformed%20into%20a%20brutal%20police%20force%20of%20a%20brutal%20colonial%20power.%20That%20is%20where%20I%20part%20away%20with%20Israel%2C%20but%20I%20emphasise%20again%2C%20that%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20question%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20legitimacy%20within%20its%201949%20armistice%20borders.%20What%20I%20reject%20totally%2C%20and%20reject%20completely%2C%20is%20the%20Zionist%20colonial%20project%20beyond%20the%20green%20line.%20And%20one%20last%20sentence%20about%20the%20ICC%2C%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20another%20illustration%20of%20Western%20double%20standards.%20The%20chief%20prosecutor%20instituted%20a%20full%20investigation%20of%20war%20crimes%20but%20the%20present%20chief%20prosecutor%20Karim%20Khan%2C%20a%20British%20barrister%2C%20has%20completely%20failed%20to%20make%20progress%20in%20that%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20when%20Russia%20invaded%20Ukraine%2C%20within%20two%20days%2C%20he%20announced%20that%20he%20was%20going%20to%20institute%20a%20war%20crimes%20investigation%2C%20and%20within%20a%20week%2C%20he%20sent%20an%20advance%20team%20to%20Kyiv%20to%20start%20gathering%20the%20evidence%20for%20a%20war%20crimes%20investigation%20and%20trial.%20So%2C%20you%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20starker%20example%20of%20Western%20hypocrisy%20than%20condoning%20everything%2C%20all%20the%20war%20crimes%20that%20Israel%20commits%2C%20but%20supporting%20the%20ICC%20in%20its%20pursuit%20of%20Russian%20war%20crimes%20in%20the%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23162231%2FGaza-building.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23162231%2FGaza-building.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23162231%2FGaza-building-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23162231%2FGaza-building-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23162231%2FGaza-building-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681396%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDamage%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20during%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%20Photo%3A%20Palestinian%20News%20%26amp%3B%20Information%20Agency%20(Wafa)%20in%20contract%20with%20APAimages%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKT%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20quick%20confirmation%20and%20one%20last%20question%20before%20I%20end.%20Do%20you%20believe%20%E2%80%93%20horrific%20and%20horrible%2C%20and%20indefensible%20as%20what%20Hamas%20did%20may%20have%20been%2C%20do%20you%20believe%20that%20the%20Israeli%20response%20on%20Gaza%20since%20October%207%20also%20constitutes%20a%20war%20crime%3F%20Also%20constitutes%20something%20that%20the%20ICC%20should%20investigate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EProfessor%20Shlaim%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EWithout%20a%20doubt%2C%20the%20current%20Israeli%20onslaught%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20constitutes%20a%20war%20crime%2C%20and%20this%20is%20nothing%20new.%20The%20first%20Israeli%20attack%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20was%20in%202008%20and%202009%2C%20and%20then%20there%20was%20the%20Goldstone%20Report%20%E2%80%93%20575%20pages%20%E2%80%93%20it%20deals%20with%2033%20episodes%2C%20and%20it%20details%20not%20one%2C%20not%20two%2C%20not%20three%2C%20but%20a%20whole%20series%20of%20Israeli%20war%20crimes%2C%20and%20Israel%20did%20not%20have%20to%20pay%20any%20price%20for%20committing%20those%20war%20crimes%20in%202008%20and%202009%2C%20or%20in%20any%20of%20the%20subsequent%20five%20attacks%20on%20Gaza.%20So%20Israel%20is%20a%20war%20criminal.%20Israel%20repeatedly%20commits%20war%20crimes%20in%20Gaza%20and%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suffer%20any%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%20My%20last%20question%20Professor%20Shlaim.%20How%20do%20people%20in%20Israel%2C%20your%20fellow%20citizens%2C%20regard%20your%20views%2C%20your%20thinking%2C%20and%20your%20comments%20on%20Israel%3F%20How%20do%20they%20respond%20when%20you%20say%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20what%20you%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20has%20committed%20murder%20on%20a%20massive%20scale%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%20You%20said%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20was%20guilty%20of%20state%20terror%2C%E2%80%9D%20you%20said%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20was%20guilty%20of%20war%20crimes%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20you%20called%20i