%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fattacks-on-us-power-grids-increase-around-elections-experts-say-2023-9%5C%22%3Epower%20plant%3C%2Fa%3E%20conveniently%20located%20on%20the%20shoreline.The%20power%20plant%20used%20ocean%20water%20to%20cool%20its%20machinery%20%E2%80%94%20so%20the%20desalination%20plant%20could%20use%20that%20hot%20saltwater%20waste%20for%20its%20main%20supply.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20person's%20trash%20is%20another's%20treasure%2C%20as%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Carlsbad%20was%20using%20water%20that%20was%20being%20extracted%20anyway%2C%20it%20posed%20no%20additional%20threat%20to%20the%20ecosystem%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20on%20the%20front%20end.%20But%20it%20did%20have%20to%20address%20the%20back%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeters%20said%20they%20developed%20a%20method%20of%20diluting%20the%20brine%20before%20sending%20it%20back%20to%20the%20shoreline%20by%20a%20discharge%20pond.%20In%20the%20eight%20years%20since%20it%20began%20running%2C%20the%20plant%20has%20kept%20salinity%20levels%20within%20regulations%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.waterboards.ca.gov%2Fwater_issues%2Fprograms%2Focean%2Fdesalination%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECalifornia%20Ocean%20Plan%20Amendments%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20set%2C%20so%20in%20that%20regard%2C%20the%20method%20worked%2C%20Peters%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20dilution%20can%20be%20an%20effective%20way%20of%20managing%20environmental%20impact%2C%20Glennon%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20other%20options%20for%20saving%20water%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224278%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photograph%20of%20the%20rows%20and%20rows%20of%20reverse%20osmosis%20machines%20at%20the%20Carlsbad%20plant.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6526bfb268f1d46f52aea5bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223209%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20many%20pumps%20that%20San%20Diego%20h