20converted%20from%20empty%20offices%20into%20luxury%20residences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20project%20will%20be%20one%20of%20Manhattan's%20most%20high-profile%20commercial-to-residential%20building%20conversions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20mayor%20recently%20unveiled%20a%20push%20to%20rezone%20large%20swaths%20of%20Manhattan%20to%20encourage%20conversions.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EForty%20lucky%20households%20will%20soon%20be%20able%20to%20call%20a%20Manhattan%20landmark%20home.%20The%20iconic%20Flatiron%20Building%20will%20be%20converted%20from%20empty%20offices%20into%20luxury%20residences%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftherealdeal.com%2Fnew-york%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Fbrodsky-to-convert-flatiron-building-to-condos%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20owners%20announced%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20tallest%20skyscrapers%20in%20the%20world%20when%20it%20was%20built%2C%20the%2022-story%2C%20120-year-old%20building%20has%20had%20a%20tumultuous%20last%20few%20years.%20It's%20been%20empty%20ever%20since%20its%20longtime%20office%20tenant%2C%20Macmillan%20Publishers%2C%20moved%20out%20of%20all%20of%20its%2020%20floors%20in%202019.%20When%20the%20property's%20owners%20couldn't%20agree%20on%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%20it%20was%20put%20up%20for%20auction%20in%20March%20of%20this%20year.%20But%20after%20it%20was%20sold%20for%20%24190%20million%2C%20the%20buyer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflatiron-building-new-owner-public-auction-2023-3%5C%22%3Efailed%20to%20pay%20the%20%2419%20million%20deposit%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20disappeared.%20Finally%2C%20the%20building%20was%20sold%20to%20one%20of%20its%20partial%20owners%2C%20real%20estate%20developer%20Jeff%20Gural%2C%20for%20%24161%20million%20in%20May%202023%20%E2%80%94%20something%20of%20a%20steal%2C%20given%20the%20structure%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F03%2F29%2Fnyregion%2Fflatiron-building-buyer.html%5C%22%3Ereportedly%2