d%2520up%25209%2525%2520sequentially.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany's%20third-quarter%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20the%20challenges%20at%20hand%20and%20are%20working%20to%20remedy%20that%2C%20which%20we%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHertz%20had%20initially%20aimed%20to%20make%2025%25%20of%20its%20fleet%20electric%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20Now%20it's%20dropping%20that%20goal.%20Today%2C%2011%25%20of%20Hertz's%20cars%20are%20electric%2C%20and%2080%25%20of%20those%20are%20Teslas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Hertz%20started%20going%20all-in%20on%20EVs%2C%20announcing%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-hertz-deal-elon-musk-advertising-marketing-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplan%20to%20buy%20100%2C000%20Teslas%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20an%20effort%20to%20give%20customers%20electric%20options.%20It%20has%20also%20inked%20deals%20with%20General%20Motors%20(to%20buy%20175%2C000%20vehicles)%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhertz-polestar-2-electric-car-rental-tesla-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEV%20brand%20Polestar%3C%2Fa%3E%20(to%20buy%2065%2C000%20vehicles)%2C%20and%20Uber%20(to%20make%20EVs%20available%20to%20drivers).%20But%20things%20haven't%20been%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERideshare%20drivers%20have%20been%20damaging%20Hertz's%20EVs%20at%20a%20higher%20rate%20than%20it%20anticipated%2C%20prompting%20the%20company%20to%20shift%20more%20EVs%20into%20its%20regular%20rental%20fleet.%20That%20led%20to%20an%20oversupply%20that%20dragged%20down%20the%20vehicles'%20revenue%20per%20day%20over%20the%20quarter%2C%20Scherr%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20Hertz%20said%20it's%20found%20that%20repairing%20damage%20to%20an%20electric%20car%20can%20cost%20around%20twice%20as%20much%20as%20fixing%20similar%20issues%20on%20a%20comparable%20combustion-engine%20vehicle.%20Routine%20maintenance%2C%20however%2C%20costs%20less%2C%20it%20said.%20(EVs%20don't%20need%20oil%20changes%20and%20are%20generally%20simpler%20to%20maintain%20than%20combustion%20vehicles.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-launches-cheaper-model-y-suv-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebarrage%20of%20price%20cuts%20over%20the%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20hasn't%20done%20Hertz%20any%20favors%20either.%20Remember%2C%20when%20Hertz%20made%20its%20Tesla%20announcement%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-says-tesla-not-signed-contract-with-hertz-yet-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20chimed%20in%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20say%20that%20he%20wasn't%20going%20to%20offer%20a%20bulk%20discount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20MSRP%20declines%20in%20EVs%20over%20the%20course%20of%202023%2C%20driven%20primarily%20by%20Tesla%2C%20have%20driven%20the%20fair%20market%20value%20of%20our%20EVs%20lower%20as%20compared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20such%20that%20a%20salvage%20creates%20a%20larger%20loss%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20greater%20burden%2C%26quot%3B%20Scherr%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdd%20it%20all%20up%2C%20and%20Hertz's%20third-quarter%20profits%20would%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20margin%20points%20higher%26quot%3B%20if%20its%20fleet%20was%20similarly%20sized%20but%20didn't%20include%20EVs%2C%20Scherr%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20nonetheless%20remain%20committed%20to%20our%20long-term%20strategy%20to%20electrify%20the%20fleet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHertz%20isn't%20the%20only%20company%20slowing%20its%20roll%20on%20EVs.%20After%20years%20of%20exponential%20sales%20growth%20and%20seemingly%20limitless%20demand%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fautomakers-over-estimated-electric-vehicle-demand-early-adopters-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric-car%20industry%20has%20hit%20a%20rough%20patch%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20ye