20registered%20on%20the%20FAA's%20%26quot%3BLimiting%20Aircraft%20Data%20Displayed%26quot%3B%20program%2C%20or%20LADD.%20The%20list%20only%20requires%20a%20one-time%20registration%20and%20prevents%20flight%20data%20from%20being%20shown%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-appears-use-faa-tool-block-jet-tracking-twitter-2022-10%5C%22%3Eflight-tracking%20websites%20like%20FlightAware%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20FlightRadar24%20that%20use%20FAA%20data%2C%20but%20they%20will%20still%20show%20up%20on%20websites%20like%20JetSpy%20that%20use%20a%20network%20of%20independent%20radios%20to%20detect%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20PIA%2C%20it's%20probably%20just%20a%20huge%20logistical%20problem%2C%20planes%20aren't%20really%20designed%20for%20you%20to%20be%20changing%20your%20code%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Sweeney%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20confusing.%20He%20really%20made%20such%20a%20big%20deal%20about%20being%20tracked.%20If%20I%20were%20him%2C%20I'd%20say%20'Why%20not%20at%20least%20try%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20left%20Shanghai%20on%20his%20private%20jet%20on%20Thursday.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64789d00df2567001837f760%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20sometimes%20makes%20multiple%20trips%20in%20a%20week%20between%20airports%20in%20California%20and%20Texas.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FAly%20Song%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FAA%20launched%20the%20PIA%20program%C2%A0in%202019%20and%20has%20issued%20390%20alternate%20ID%20codes%20since%20the%20program%20began%2C%20an%20FAA%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fjeremybogaisky%2F2023%2F10%2F25%2Felon-musk-may-have-given-up-on-privacy-fo