ess%20they%20are%20against%20the%20law.%20But%20it%20is%20certainly%20not%20in%20good%20taste.%20A%20civil%20servant%E2%80%99s%20job%20is%20to%20implement%20government%20schemes%20and%20deliver%20services.%20At%20best%2C%20if%20there%20are%20issues%20of%20coordination%20with%20the%20states%2C%20officers%20can%20put%20out%20their%20contact%20details%20but%20that%20is%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties.%20As%20cabinet%20secretary%2C%20I%20would%20take%20secretaries%20of%20various%20departments%20by%20the%20planeloads%20to%20the%20various%20states%2C%20especially%20the%20weaker%20states%20for%20better%20coordination%20between%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20and%20better%20delivery%20of%20services.%20We%20would%20resolve%20problems%20on%20the%20spot.%20That%20in%20short%20is%20the%20job%20of%20a%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20politicians%20like%20BJP%20IT%20Cell%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20say%20that%20bureaucrats%20must%20serve%20the%20people%20as%20the%20government%20deems%20fit.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20job%20is%20not%20to%20showcase%20or%20celebrate%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20government.%20While%20this%20order%20of%20Rath%20Prabharis%20is%20per%20se%20not%20illegal%2C%20it%20is%20definitely%20in%20bad%20taste.%20Projecting%20anyone%20in%20this%20manner%20is%20extraordinary%20and%20I%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20something%20like%20this%20in%20my%20entire%20career.%20Anyway%2C%20officials%20at%20the%20level%20of%20deputy%20director%20or%20director%20are%20too%20junior%20and%20have%20the%20power%20to%20only%20put%20up%20files.%20They%20cannot%20take%20a%20decision%20or%20resolve%20a%20problem%20on%20the%20ground.%20So%20just%20reading%20out%20from%20a%20written%20piece%20of%20paper%20is%20not%20something%20that%20officers%20should%20be%20doing.%20This%20is%20most%20unusual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20another%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20which%20says%20that%20soldiers%20on%20leave%20must%20showcase%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20government.%20So%20this%20is%20not%20just%20about%20government%20servants.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20again%20is%20a%20ridiculous%20order.%20When%20a%20person%20is%20on%20leave%2C%20they%20cannot%20be%20tasked%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20orders.%20The%20government%20can%20only%20request.%20And%20even%20then%2C%20how%20can%20such%20an%20order%20be%20implemented%3F%20Who%20will%20monitor%20and%20how%20will%20the%20soldier%20know%20the%20fine%20details%20of%20the%20schemes%20of%20the%20government%3F%20If%20a%20person%20is%20on%20leave%2C%20he%20or%20she%20is%20on%20leave.%20If%20a%20person%20is%20asked%20to%20carry%20out%20these%20orders%20then%20he%20or%20she%20cannot%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20on%20leave.%20Again%20a%20highly%20improper%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20were%20cabinet%20secretary%20now%2C%20what%20would%20you%20do%3F%20And%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20criticise%20when%20an%20officer%20has%20retired%20but%20it%20is%20quite%20a%20different%20thing%20when%20the%20officer%20is%20serving.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20can%20only%20share%20an%20anecdote%20of%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20Once%20I%20called%20the%20prime%20minister%20about%20an%20appointment%20of%20a%20special%20director%20to%20the%20CBI.%20A%20junior%20officer%20was%20being%20appointed%2C%20overlooking%20the%20seniority%20of%20another.%20The%20prime%20minister%20was%20eating%20lunch.%20He%20halted%20his%20meal%2C%20heard%20me%20out%20and%20left%20his%20lunch%20unfinished.%20A%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20(the%20advisor%20to%20the%20prime%20minister)%20T.K.A.%20Nair%2C%20who%20said%20the%20prime%20minister%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20We%20reached%207%2C%20Race%20Course%20Road%2C%20where%20Pulok%20Chatterjee%20(also%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20prime%20minister)%20was%20already%20waiting.%20The%20prime%20minister%20immediately%20worked%20out%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20senior%20CBI%20officer%20and%20gave%20orders%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20Minister%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20to%20do%20the%20needful.%20I%20am%20not%20sure%20if%20anyone%20can%20even%20tell%20the%20present%20prime%20minister%20that%20he%20is%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698481545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28134832%2Fkm-chand.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-servants-rath-prabharis-km-chandrasekhar-interview%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20spoke%20to%20K.M.%20Chandrasekhar%20about%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20Modi%20government%20asking%20ministries%20to%20nominate%20civil%20servants%20as%20'Rath%20Prabharis'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-servants-rath-prabharis-km-chandrasekhar-interview%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%20appears%20to%20show%20Israeli%20ground%20forces%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698480242000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F161A7%2Fproduction%2F_131553509_p0gpbrh9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67248398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dozens%20of%20tanks%20and%20military%20vehicles%20are%20seen%20in%20footage%20released%20by%20the%20IDF.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A51%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-middle-east-67248398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%2010%20Years%2C%20Total%20Cargo%20Handled%20by%20Adani%20Ports%20Jumped%20Nearly%20Fourfold%20to%20337%20MT%20in%20FY23%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FAdani_Mundra_Port_Kutch_Gujarat1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20as%20many%20as%2014%20ports%20and%20terminals%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20handles%20a%20quarter%20of%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fadani-ports-handles-highest-ever-rail-cargo-fy23-8613993%2F%5C%22%3Ecargo%20passing%20through%20India%E2%80%99s%20ports%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fon-average-an-adani-port-every-500-km-of-coastline-these-handle-24-of-all-cargo-govt-share-dips-9002772%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlong%20India%E2%80%99s%205%2C422-kilometre%20coastline%2C%20Adani%20has%20a%20presence%20every%20500%20km%20on%20an%20average%2C%20from%20just%20a%20blip%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20far%20western%20end%2010%20years%20ago%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20top%20officials%2C%20including%20a%20former%20competition%20regulator%2C%20have%20flagged%20risks%20of%20market%20concentration%20in%20the%20ports%20industry%2C%20highlighting%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20phenomenal%20expansion%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%2010%20years%2C%20the%20total%20cargo%20handled%20by%20Adani%20ports%20jumped%20nearly%20fourfold%20to%20337%20million%20tonnes%20in%20FY23.%20Its%20volumes%20grew%20at%20a%20compounded%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%2014%25%20against%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%204%25.%20If%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20share%20is%20removed%2C%20the%20latter%20figure%20falls%20to%20barely%202.7%25%2C%20the%20newspaper%20said%20in%20its%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20group%E2%80%99s%20market%20share%20in%20total%20cargo%20handled%20has%20nearly%20tripled%20from%20around%209%25%20in%202013%20to%20about%2024%25%20in%202023%3B%20that%20of%20Central%20government-controlled%20ports%20dropped%20to%20around%2054.5%25%20from%2058.5%25%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmongst%20ports%20that%20are%20not%20under%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20market%20share%20has%20crossed%20the%2050%25%20mark%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20Ltd%20(APSEZ)%E2%80%99s%20coastal%20network%20competes%20with%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20over%2012%20ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20part%20of%20the%20rise%20in%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20market%20share%20in%20the%20ports%20sector%20%E2%80%93%20from%209%25%20to%2024%25%20in%2010%20years%20%E2%80%93%20has%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20Union%20government-controlled%20ports%20(called%20%E2%80%98major%20ports%E2%80%99%20in%20industry%20parlance)%20whose%20cargo%20share%20has%20fallen%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20top%20economic%20ministry%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Inorganic%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20Behind%20the%20Purchase%20of%20Gangavaram%20Port%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20section%20of%20government%20officials%20and%20regulators%20pointed%20out%C2%A0that%20this%20growth%20has%20been%20through%20the%20inorganic%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCargo%20handling%20data%20analysed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%20that%20the%20ports%20acquired%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group%20account%20for%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20the%20total%20cargo%20volumes%20(123.7%20million%20tonnes%20of%20337%20million%20tonnes%2C%20or%2037%25)%20handled%20by%20the%20company.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20a%20growth%20model%20compounds%20the%20concerns%20about%20the%20growing%20concentration%20risk%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20same%20official%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20dominance%20of%20a%20single%20player%20along%20the%20entire%20coastline%2C%20from%20west%20to%20east%2C%20could%20potentially%20lead%20to%20a%20gradual%20weakening%20of%20the%20negotiating%20leverage%20held%20by%20shipping%20companies%2C%20particularly%20in%20certain%20geographic%20regions%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221097%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit.jpg%201097w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit-300x186.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit-1024x635.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681723%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22680%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGautam%20Adani.%20Photo%3A%20Photo%3A%20US%20Department%20of%20State%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20Public%20domain%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%20top%20officials%20flag%20concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20with%20the%20shipping%20ministry%20flagged%20these%20concerns%2C%20highlighting%20risks%20of%20low%20competition%2C%20high%20entry%20barriers%20for%20newer%20and%20smaller%20players%2C%20high%20dependencies%20on%20dominant%20players%2C%20and%20higher%20chances%20of%20abuse%20of%20dominant%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20official%20from%20an%20economic%20ministry%2C%20who%20also%20requested%20anonymity%2C%20further%20expressed%20that%20what%20has%20heightened%20concerns%20regarding%20this%20market%20consolidation%20in%20a%20critical%20industry%20like%20shipping%20is%20the%20context%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fwhy-has-the-adani-hindenburg-issue-become-a-matter-of-national-concern%5C%22%3Eallegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20related%20to%20accounting%20fraud%20and%20stock%20manipulation%20concerning%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20allegations%20were%20made%20by%20the%20US-based%20short-seller%20Hindenburg%20Research%20in%20January%20this%20year%20and%20have%20more%20recently%20surfaced%20in%20reports%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ffull-text-former-sebi-chief-says-ft-occrp-adani-story-very-persuasive%5C%22%3Edocuments%3C%2Fa%3E%20obtained%20by%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%2C%20which%20were%20then%20shared%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-group-stocks-offshore-investments-reports%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-coal-imports-over-pricing-customers-overcharged-fuel-ft%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fcompanies%2Fadani-mauritius-based-fund-deny-allegations-by-occrp%2Farticle67255759.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Adani%2520group%2520on%2520Thursday%2Cthrough%2520opaque%2520funds%2520based%2520in%5C%22%3Ehas%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fadani-group-rejects-hindenburg-allegations-in-notice-to-investors%2Farticleshow%2F97405099.cms%5C%22%3Edenied%3C%2Fa%3E%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20former%20chairperson%20of%20Competition%20Commission%20of%20India%20(CCI)%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20while%20ports%20may%20be%20considered%20natural%20monopolies%20at%20a%20broad%20level%2C%20there%20are%20issues%20with%20this.%20%E2%80%9CIts%20(APSEZ%E2%80%99s)%20share%20has%20been%20continuously%20growing%20in%20a%20creeping%20fashion.%20It%20is%20definitely%20a%20concern%20if%20there%20is%20a%20creeping%20acquisition%20of%20capacity%20by%20one%20player%20while%20the%20others%20fall%20or%20languish.%20It%20may%20not%20be%20too%20glaring%20now%20but%20down%20the%20line%2C%20say%20in%20five%20to%2010%20years%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20problem.%20The%20government%20and%20the%20CCI%20should%20keep%20an%20eye%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20CCI%20head%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Inorganic%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20Behind%20the%20Purchase%20of%20Gangavaram%20Port%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuick%20expansion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20in%20FY13%2C%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20ports%20business%20had%20cargo%20volumes%20of%20around%2091%20million%20tonnes%2C%20accounting%20for%20just%2010%25%20of%20the%20cumulative%20cargo%20volumes%20handled%20by%20all%20ports.%20Over%2023%25%20of%20the%20cargo%20volumes%20were%20handled%20by%20all%20minor%20ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20a%20port%20is%20a%20minor%20port%20if%20it%20is%20not%20government%20controlled.%20The%20nomenclature%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20size%20of%20the%20port%20or%20cargo%20volumes%20handled.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20the%20Adani-owned%20Mundra%20Port%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20a%20minor%20port%20%E2%80%93%20handled%20the%20most%20cargo%20at%20155%20million%20tonnes%20in%20FY23%2C%20more%20than%20any%20of%20the%2012%20Union%20government-owned%20ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20FY23%2C%20the%20minor%20ports%20handled%20close%20to%20650%20million%20tonnes%20in%20cargo.%20APSEZ%20handled%20around%20337%20million%20tonnes%20in%20volume%2C%20crossing%20the%20505%20mark%2C%20as%20mentioned%20earlier.%20These%20cargoes%20primarily%20came%20from%20its%20eight%20operational%20minor%20ports%20in%20India%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20these%2010%20years%2C%20APSEZ%E2%80%99s%20cargo%20volumes%20were%20higher%20than%20the%20volumes%20handled%20by%20major%20ports%20and%20minor%20ports%20in%20most%20years%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20in%20FY21%2C%20when%20India%E2%80%99s%20overall%20port%20volumes%2C%20and%20volumes%20at%20major%20and%20minor%20ports%20contracted%20by%20over%204%25%20year-on-year%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20APSEZ%E2%80%99s%20volumes%20were%20up%20nearly%2011%25%20over%20the%20previous%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFuelling%20the%20ASPEZ%20expansion%20was%20a%20series%20of%20acquisitions%3A%20Dhamra%20in%20Odisha%3B%20Kattupalli%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3B%20Krishnapatnam%20and%20Gangavaram%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3B%20and%20Dighi%20in%20Maharashtra.%20In%20FY23%2C%20APSEZ%E2%80%99s%20non-Mundra%20volumes%20accounted%20for%2054%25%20of%20its%20overall%20port%20cargo%2C%20having%20grown%20at%20a%20CAGR%20of%20around%2036%25%20since%20FY13%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20has%20seen%20rapid%20growth%20across%20a%20few%20other%20sectors%20as%20well.%20It%20is%20the%20largest%20private%20sector%20airport%20operator%20in%20India.%20It%20oversees%20eight%20airports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20has%20also%20become%20the%20largest%20cement%20manufacturer%20and%20private%20sector%20thermal%20power%20producer%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698479469000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FAdani_Mundra_Port_Kutch_Gujarat1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fin-10-years-total-cargo-handled-by-adani-ports-jumped-nearly-fourfold-to-337-mt-in-fy23-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20as%20many%20as%2014%20ports%20and%20terminals%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20handles%20a%20quarter%20of%20all%20cargo%20passing%20through%20India%E2%80%99s%20ports%2C%20the%20Indian%20Express%20has%20reported.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20government's%20share%20has%20dropped%20to%20around%2054.5%25%20from%2058.5%25%20in%202013.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fin-10-years-total-cargo-handled-by-adani-ports-jumped-nearly-fourfold-to-337-mt-in-fy23-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Backstory%3A%20What%20Was%20the%20Indian%20Media%20Doing%20When%20a%20Genocide%20Was%20Playing%20Out%20in%20Gaza%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08162927%2FScreenshot-2022-06-08-at-4.29.23-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20horrendous%20Hamas%20incursion%20into%20Israel%20which%20targeted%20civilians%2C%20including%20women%2C%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%2C%20will%20remain%20in%20global%20consciousness%20as%20a%20crime%20against%20humanity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20swiftly%20followed%20those%20brutal%20assaults%20of%20October%207%20was%20the%20unremitting%20aerial%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%2C%20killing%20thousands%20of%20unarmed%20people%2C%20including%20women%2C%20children%20and%20the%20elderly%2C%20as%20part%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20drive%20to%20seek%20%E2%80%9Cjustice%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20back%20story%20here%20of%20colonisation%2C%20forced%20expulsion%20of%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20capture%20of%20their%20land.%20It%20has%20remained%20a%20blot%20on%20the%20West%20which%20had%20sought%20to%20assuage%20its%20guilt%20over%20the%20Nazi%20atrocities%20perpetrated%20on%20the%20Jews%20by%20making%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20who%20had%20no%20role%20in%20the%20Holocaust%2C%20pay%20the%20greatest%20price%20for%20it%20through%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Jewish%20state%20of%20Israel%20on%20Palestinian%20soil.%20Over%20time%2C%20Israel%20evolved%20into%20a%20settler%20colonial%20apartheid%20state%2C%20capturing%20more%20and%20more%20of%20Palestinian%20land%20through%20untold%2C%20militarised%20repression%20until%20it%20has%20become%20what%20it%20is%20today%3A%20a%20nuclear%20power%20with%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20powerful%20armies%2C%20enabled%20by%20the%20steady%20drip%20of%20%243.8%20billion%20from%20the%20US%20pouring%20in%20as%20military%20aid%20every%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20this%20back%20story%20was%20known%20in%20India%3B%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Indian%20political%20establishment%20extended%20solidarity%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%20That%20time%20has%20long%20passed%20and%20nothing%20indicated%20this%20better%20than%20India%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3Eabstained%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20a%20UNGA%20resolution%20on%20October%2027%2C%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20truce%20in%20Gaza.%20Remember%2C%20that%20three-day%20visit%20to%20Israel%20that%20Narendra%20Modi%20made%20in%202017%20%E2%80%93%20the%20first%20Indian%20prime%20minister%20to%20do%20so%3F%20And%20how%20he%20followed%20it%20up%20with%20a%20three-hour%20visit%20to%20Ramallah%20the%20next%20year%3F%20The%20brevity%20of%20the%20latter%20visit%20and%20the%20statement%20which%20emanated%20from%20it%20signalled%20to%20the%20world%20that%20the%20careful%20balance%20India%20had%20hitherto%20maintained%20in%20its%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20entities%20had%20ended.%20Today%2C%20India%20is%20one%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20most%20crucial%20trading%20partners.%20More%20relevant%2C%20it%20is%20the%20largest%20purchaser%20of%20Israel-made%20arms%2C%20apart%20from%20surveillance%20technology%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fimport-data-ib-israel-nso-pegasus-occrp%23%3A~%3Atext%3DScience%2520About%2520Us-%2CImport%2520Data%2520Shows%2520IB%2520Bought%2520Hardware%2520From%2520Israel%2520Matching%2520Kit%2Cof%2520a%2520major%2520defence%2520deal.%5C%22%3EImport%20Data%20Shows%20IB%20Bought%20Hardware%20From%20Israel%20Matching%20Kit%20Used%20for%20Pegasus%2C%20OCCRP%20Says%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20October%2020%2C%202022).%20It%20has%20also%20emerged%20as%20the%20Indian%20establishment%E2%80%99s%20most%20favoured%20model%20for%20military%20and%20police%20deployment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECultural%20and%20media%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20grown%20apace.%20The%20Mumbai%20attacks%20of%202008%2C%20which%20included%20strikes%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EChabad%20Lubavitch%20establishment%2C%20were%20something%20of%20a%20tipping%20point.%20That%20story%20had%20many%20facets%20which%20resonated%20in%20the%20country.%20An%20Indian%20nanny%20who%20rescued%20a%20toddler%20from%20the%20attackers%20became%20a%20major%20news%20point.%20Even%20more%20pervasive%20was%20the%20projection%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccommon%20threat%20of%20terror%20from%20hostile%20neighbours%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Modi%20years%20have%20seen%20this%20slant%20acquire%20a%20seriously%20communal%20tone%2C%20playing%20as%20it%20does%20to%20the%20anti-Muslim%20ideological%20project%20of%20Hindutva.%20It%20is%20this%20trope%20that%20once%20again%20seems%20to%20be%20reflected%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20tweet%20on%20October%207%3A%20%E2%80%9CDeeply%20shocked%20by%20the%20news%20of%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel.%20Our%20thoughts%20and%20prayers%20are%20with%20the%20innocent%20victims%20and%20their%20families.%20We%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Israel%20at%20this%20difficult%20hour.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20was%20quick%20to%20respond%20to%20this%20warmth%20and%20before%20long%20%E2%80%98India%20is%20with%20Israel%E2%80%99%2C%20was%20not%20just%20trending%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20but%20came%20to%20reflect%20a%20larger%20global%20common%20sense.%20Despite%20a%20later%20attempt%20at%20publicly%20acknowledging%20the%20suffering%20of%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20and%20the%20dispatch%20of%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Gaza%2C%20the%20well-defined%20reality%20is%20that%20%E2%80%98India%20is%20with%20Israel%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20been%20deepened%20by%20two%20layers%20of%20media%20coverage%3A%20first%2C%20the%20social%20media%20blitzkrieg%20in%20support%20of%20Israel%20after%20the%20October%20Hamas%20attacks%20and%20second%2C%20the%20embedding%20of%20major%20television%20channels%20within%20the%20Israeli%20army%20information%20machinery.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20to%20the%20first%20aspect%2C%20the%20surge%20of%20pro-Israeli%2C%20pro-bombardment%20sentiment%20from%20online%20Indians%20signals%20a%20major%20internationalisation%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20troll.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fs