2026)%20underlines%20this%3A%20%E2%80%9CPernicious%20hatred%20for%20Muslims%20is%20the%20glue%20which%20binds%20them%20with%20the%20Israeli%20narrative.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20question%20I%20want%20to%20ask%2C%20while%20coming%20to%20the%20second%20aspect%2C%20is%20this%3A%20When%20did%20channels%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20get%20embedded%20in%20the%20Israeli%20army%3F%20Some%2020%20days%20after%20the%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0attack%2C%20when%20Gaza%20was%20witnessing%20genocide%2C%20they%20were%20still%20flogging%20the%20broken%20window%20panes%20and%20rotting%20potatoes%20left%20behind%20in%20a%20deserted%20kibbutz.%20There%20was%20some%20kind%20of%20competition%20between%20these%20two%20channels%3A%20if%20one%20had%20discovered%20the%20potatoes%20earlier%2C%20the%20other%20reported%20there%20were%20potatoes%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20fruit%20left%20behind.%20Their%20coverage%20could%20have%20been%20termed%20pure%20burlesque%20if%20it%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20so%20dangerously%20the%20media%20equivalent%20of%20Nero.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20script%20they%20used%20sometimes%20appeared%20to%20be%20expanded%20social%20media%20posts.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20really%20happened%3F%20Because%20of%20the%20heavy%20rocket%20fire%20from%20Hamas%E2%80%A6%20look%20at%20the%20glass%2C%20look%20at%20the%20roof.%20This%20means%20they%20tried%20to%20target%20each%20and%20every%20person%20in%20the%20house%E2%80%A6%20Look%20at%20the%20condition%20here.%20The%20streets%20are%20almost%20deserted.%20Nobody%20is%20here%E2%80%A6%20Some%20shoes%20are%20lying%20here%2C%20uniforms%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27180005%2F2048px-2017.03.26_Anti-Israel_Protest_Washington_DC_USA_01949_32857528933.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27180005%2F2048px-2017.03.26_Anti-Israel_Protest_Washington_DC_USA_01949_32857528933.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27180005%2F2048px-2017.03.26_Anti-Israel_Protest_Washington_DC_USA_01949_32857528933-300x175.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27180005%2F2048px-2017.03.26_Anti-Israel_Protest_Washington_DC_USA_01949_32857528933-1024x596.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682127%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22698%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFlags%20of%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Ted%20Eytan%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%202.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20some%20truly%20cringe-worthy%20moments%20as%20well.%20One%20correspondent%20while%20interviewing%20Israeli%20MP%2C%20Sharren%20Haskel%2C%20slipped%20in%20a%20little%20speech%20about%20how%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20Pakistani%20terror%20too.%E2%80%9D%20He%20then%20went%20back%20to%20ask%20her%20what%20Israel%20was%20doing%20to%20strike%20at%20the%20root%20of%20Hamas.%20Haskel%2C%20nothing%20loathe%2C%20launched%20into%20a%20description%20of%20Iran%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Chead%20of%20the%20snake%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20coverage%20was%20so%20over-the-top%3B%20so%20out%20of%20whack%20with%20journalistic%20methods%20and%20ethics%2C%20that%20it%20appeared%20at%20times%20to%20be%20pure%2C%20old-fashioned%20paid%20news.%20In%20fact%2C%20their%20own%20script%20indicated%20that%20all%20the%20information%20they%20were%20putting%20out%20came%20directly%20from%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20sources.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20Now%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reporter%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20been%20given%20a%20manual%20by%20Israel%20with%20images%20which%20were%20televised%20promptly%20for%20Indian%20audiences.%20His%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20counterpart%20was%20handed%20over%20a%20tape%20comprising%2043%20minutes%20of%20footage%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attacks.%20Going%20through%20it%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20harrowing%20experiences%20of%20his%20life.%20He%20then%20proceeded%20to%20describe%20each%20frame%2C%20the%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%9CAllahu%20Akbar%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20killing%20of%20a%20black%20Labrador%2C%20a%20man%20being%20killed%20before%20his%20two%20sons%E2%80%A6%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20saw%20%E2%80%93%20completely%20charred%20infants.%20Women%20with%20gunshot%20wounds%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20An%20audio%20tape%20of%20a%20Hamas%20operative%20talking%20excitedly%20to%20his%20parents%20about%20having%20killed%20ten%20Israelis%20and%20the%20father%20congratulating%20him%20was%20telecast%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20just%20as%20were%20the%20visuals%20from%20the%20Kibbutz%20Be%E2%80%99eri%20and%20the%20site%20of%20the%20Tribe%20of%20Nova%20Music%20Festival.%20What%20was%20striking%20about%20them%20was%20that%20they%20were%20essentially%20vignettes%20%E2%80%93%20the%20entire%20flow%20of%20each%20event%20was%20completely%20lost%20to%20the%20viewer.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20intended%20to%20underestimate%20the%20horrendous%20nature%20of%20the%20October%207%20attacks%2C%20but%20as%20an%20argument%20for%20reporting%20the%20story%20as%20it%20needed%20to%20be%20reported%2C%20because%20even%20as%20these%20gentlemen%20told%20their%20recycled%20news%20stories%2C%20day%20after%20day%2C%20Gaza%20was%20being%20bombed%20to%20a%20stage%20when%20living%2C%20breathing%20people%20were%20visibly%20at%20death%E2%80%99s%20door.%20Yet%20the%20horror%20in%20Gaza%20remained%20a%20small%20sideshow%20in%20their%20news%20tableaux%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20understand%20that%20these%20channels%20could%20not%20report%20from%20Gaza%2C%20but%20what%20stopped%20them%20from%20uprooting%20themselves%20from%20Kibutz%20Be%E2%80%99eri%20and%20talking%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20refugees%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20Jordan%2C%20for%20instance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20media%20of%20even%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20closest%20allies%20never%20stooped%20to%20this%20level%20of%20completely%20one-sided%20coverage.%20The%20Western%20media%20were%20controlled%20without%20doubt%2C%20they%20were%20deeply%20biased%20towards%20Israel%20clearly%2C%20but%20somewhere%20journalistic%20professionalism%20was%20not%20completely%20abandoned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20time%20will%20come%20when%20the%20Indian%20media%20will%20be%20left%20facing%20a%20deeply%20uncomfortable%20question%3A%20What%20were%20you%20doing%20when%20a%20genocide%20was%20playing%20out%20in%20Gaza%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ERelease%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20Amit%20Chakravarty%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDoes%20every%20generation%20have%20to%20face%20an%20emergency%3F%20This%20is%20a%20question%20raised%20by%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20in%20his%20new%20book%20(written%20before%20his%20recent%20incarceration)%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKeeping%20Up%20The%20Good%20Fight%20From%20the%20Emergency%20to%20the%20Present%20Day%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20emergency%20then%20and%20the%20situation%20now%2C%20he%20describes%2C%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdestructive%20situation%20that%20develops%20if%20the%20political%20dispensation%20of%20the%20time%20erodes%20people%E2%80%99s%20fundamental%20rights%20in%20numerous%20ways%E2%80%9D.%20The%20erosion%20can%20take%20several%20forms.%20Yet%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmuzzle%20a%20million%20or%20more%20people%2C%20you%20cannot%20use%20the%20Emergency%20instrument%2C%20which%20was%20direct%20censorship%E2%80%A6%20The%20new%20censors%20%E2%80%93%20official%20and%20unofficial%20%E2%80%93%20make%20an%20example%20of%20a%20few%20to%20create%20a%20chilling%20effect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20precisely%20was%20what%20the%20swoop%20on%20nearly%2050%20journalists%20and%20associates%20of%20the%20news%20portal%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20October%203%2C%20aimed%20to%20do.%20It%20revealed%20to%20us%20once%20again%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cnew%20censors%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%20the%20Special%20Cell%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20%E2%80%93%20are%20riding%20roughshod%20over%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20citizens%20with%20absolute%20impunity%20in%20order%20to%20send%20out%20their%20chilling%20message.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EViolation%20of%20privacy%20was%20arguably%20one%20of%20the%20most%20distressing%20aspects%20of%20that%20raid.%20Here%20we%20are%20speaking%20not%20just%20about%20their%20personal%20privacy%20%E2%80%93%20the%20incursion%20into%20their%20homes%2C%20the%20ransacking%20and%20seizure%20of%20books%2C%20documents%20and%20personal%20papers%20%E2%80%93%20but%20their%20digital%20privacy.%20Devices%20like%20mobile%20phones%2C%20laptops%2C%20and%20desktops%20%E2%80%93%20critical%20for%20journalistic%20work%20and%20the%20protection%20of%20sources%20%E2%80%93%20were%20taken%20away.%20The%20asymmetric%20power%20between%20police%20personnel%20and%20the%20ordinary%20citizen%20is%20so%20stark%20that%20most%20of%20those%20so%20raided%20surrendered%20without%20demur%20sensitive%20information%20like%20pin%20numbers%20and%20passwords%20of%20their%20digital%20devices%2C%20along%20with%20the%20devices%20themselves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20standard%20practice%20is%20that%20once%20seized%2C%20devices%20are%20rarely%20returned.%20This%20was%20why%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-journalists-seized-press-freedom-delhi-court-the-wire%5C%22%3Erecent%20court%20judgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EWire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20case%2C%20ordering%20the%20police%20to%20release%20devices%20taken%20from%20the%20homes%20of%20its%20editors%20and%20managers%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20is%20so%20important.%20The%20court%20ruled%20that%20devices%2C%20for%20which%20mirror%20images%20were%20anyway%20available%20with%20the%20police%2C%20cannot%20be%20kept%20indefinitely%20by%20the%20investigating%20officer%20%E2%80%9Conly%20on%20the%20speculation%20of%20an%20uncertain%20future%20event%2Fdiscovery.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20at%20stake%20here%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPuttaswamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20verdict%20delivered%20by%20a%20nine-judge%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20in%202017%2C%20which%20recognised%20digital%20privacy%20as%20well%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20modern%20notions%20of%20privacy%20in%20the%20digital%20age%20use%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98privacy%E2%80%99%20as%20shorthand%20to%20refer%20to%20a%20bundle%20of%20several%20concomitant%20rights%20over%20personal%20information%20%E2%80%93%20the%20right%20of%20access%2C%20the%20right%20of%20erasure%2C%20the%20right%20to%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20manner%20of%20its%20processing%2C%20the%20right%20of%20accuracy%2C%20the%20right%20of%20control%20of%20third-party%20access%2C%20etc.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-seizures-making-a-mockery-of-landmark-privacy-ruling%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2520held%2520that%2520privacy%2520in%2Cof%2520the%2520right%2520to%2520privacy.%5C%22%3EDevice%20Seizures%20Are%20Making%20a%20Mockery%20of%20The%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20Landmark%20Privacy%20Ruling%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20October%2017).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMadhavi%20Goradia%20Divan%2C%20in%20a%20recent%20newspaper%20comment%2C%20cites%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVirendra%20Khanna%20vs%20State%20of%20Karnataka%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20judgment%2C%20which%20set%20down%20how%20mobile%20records%20must%20be%20investigated.%20It%20ruled%20that%20the%20investigating%20officer%20must%20first%20seek%20court%20directions%20and%20emphasised%20that%20there%20must%20be%20reasonable%20ground%20for%20believing%20that%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20a%20search.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eraids%20only%20make%20more%20crucial%20the%20issues%20raised%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPuttaswamy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVirendra%20Khanna%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20verdicts.%20Now%20a%20petition%20by%20five%20academics%20is%20slated%20to%20come%20up%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20November.%20They%20have%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20draw%20up%20norms%20under%20which%20search%20and%20seizure%20operations%20by%20the%20police%20and%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20can%20be%20conducted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20chilling%20message%20sent%20to%20journalists%20by%20those%20raids%20continues%20to%20linger.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftopic%2Fdelhi-court%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDelhi%20court%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20ordered%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftopic%2Fprabir-purkayastha%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPrabir%20Purkayastha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20human%20resources%20department%20head%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftopic%2Famit-chakravarty%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAmit%20Chakravarty%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20who%20is%20disabled%20and%20suffering%20gravely%2C%20remain%20in%20police%20custody%20in%20a%20completely%20fallacious%20case%20accusing%20them%20of%20spreading%20Chinese%20propaganda.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJournalists%20across%20the%20country%20are%20following%20both%20cases%20very%20closely%20because%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20their%20human%20and%20professional%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F26081747%2FIMG_4150-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F26081747%2FIMG_4150-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F26081747%2FIMG_4150-1-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F26081747%2FIMG_4150-1-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-542498%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%20case%20appalling%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ERadha%20Kumar%2C%20policy%20analyst%20and%20author%2C%20comments%20on%20the%20repression%20against%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20appalling%20arrests%20of%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20Amit%20Chakrabarty%20under%20the%20UAPA%20is%20the%20latest%20of%20a%20series%20of%20attacks%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20the%20media.%20I%20hope%20all%20opposition%20parties%20will%20now%20pledge%20to%20defend%20the%20independence%20of%20media%2C%20such%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20withdraw%20the%20UAPA%20and%20similar%20laws%20that%20are%20used%20to%20victimise%20human%20rights%20defenders.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESolidarity%20with%20Palestine%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKhushi%20Kabir%2C%20advisor%2C%20sent%20in%20this%20statement%20of%20Sangat%2C%20a%20South%20Asian%20Feminist%20Network%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CSangat%2C%20a%20feminist%20network%20representing%20women%20from%20different%20countries%20in%20South%20Asia%2C%20stands%20against%20the%20genocide%20in%20Gaza.%20Thousands%20of%20innocent%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%20by%20the%20aggression%20carried%20out%20by%20Israeli%20Occupation%20Forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20acknowledge%20and%20share%20the%20pain%20and%20horror%20of%20the%20families%2C%20victims%2C%20and%20hostages%20of%20the%20October%207%20violence%20by%20Hamas.%20This%20action%20by%20Palestinian%20resistance%20has%20to%20be%20seen%20in%20light%20of%20the%20atrocities%20the%20citizens%20of%20brutally%20occupied%20Gaza%20have%20been%20subjugated%20to%20in%20all%20these%20years.%20It%20has%20been%20nothing%20but%20an%20open%20prison%20with%20severe%20restrictions%20on%20food%2C%20water%2C%20livelihood%2C%20and%20mobility.%20Palestinians%20in%20Gaza%20have%20been%20treated%20as%20less%20than%20humans%2C%20totally%20violating%20their%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20alarmed%20by%20the%20support%20of%20various%20heads%20of%20state%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Israel%2C%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20despite%20his%20declared%20strategy%20for%20eradicating%20and%20annihilating%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20through%20an%20immoral%20war.%20We%20are%20particularly%20concerned%20about%20the%20genocidal%20pitched%20statements%20from%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20lawmakers%20and%20the%20extremely%20racist%20and%20dehumanised%20language%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20and%20the%20ongoing%20wanton%20military%20assault%20on%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20call%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20offensive%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Israel%20on%20innocent%20men%2C%20women%2C%20and%20children.%20We%20demand%20an%20immediate%20end%20to%20what%20is%20a%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%20and%20reiterate%20that%20intentional%20starvation%20of%20the%20civilian%20population%20is%20a%20crime%20against%20humanity%2C%20which%20is%20being%20committed%20against%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20with%20total%20impunity.%20A%20humanitarian%20corridor%20must%20be%20opened%20immediately%2C%20and%20electricity%20and%20water%20must%20be%20reinstated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20urgently%20demand%20that%20the%20leaders%20of%20nations%20supporting%20Israel%20understand%20that%20what%20is%20unfolding%20is%20a%20genocide.%20There%20can%20be%20no%20excuse%20ever%20for%20violence%20with%20this%20intent.%20Support%20for%20it%20is%20clearly%20indicative%20of%20a%20brutal%20colonial%20mindset.%20Revenge%20is%20not%20justice%E2%80%A6%20We%20call%20for%20the%20institution%20of%20proper%20mechanisms%20for%20accountability%20and%20justice%20to%20end%20this%20culture%20of%20immunity%20and%20impunity%20for%20violations%20of%20International%20Humanitarian%20Law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSangat%20believes%20that%20the%20feminist%20struggle%20for%20social%20justice%2C%20equality%2C%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20peace%20includes%20a%20people%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20self-%20determination%2C%20and%20we%20join%20our%20Palestinian%20sisters%2C%20brothers%2C%20and%20allies%20across%20the%20world%20in%20condemning%20this%20ongoing%20genocidal%20war%20and%20call%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESathyanand%20from%20the%20CPI%20Bangalore%20District%20Committee%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CProtestors%20of%20the%20Left%20parties%20speaking%20out%20against%20Israel%20atrocities%20in%20Palestine%20were%20arrested%20by%20Bangalore%20police%20in%20Freedom%20Park.%20The%20permission%20was%20denied%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20lack%20of%20space%20in%20Freedom%20Park.%20However%2C%20the%20real%20reason%20is%20that%20the%20police%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20stop%20any%20protests%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%C2%A0%20We%20condemn%20the%20high-handed%20attitude%20of%20the%20State%20government%20to%20stifle%20all%20voices%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20We%20condemn%20the%20Central%20government%E2%80%99s%20support%20of%20Israel%20and%20the%20dilution%20of%20our%20historic%20support%20for%20Palestine.%C2%A0%20We%20stand%20firmly%20in%20favour%20of%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%20and%20the%20immediate%20implementation%20of%20the%20two-state%20formula.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20real%20reason%20for%20October%207%20attack%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EM.K.%20Shah%20sent%20this%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20Ilan%20Berman%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20think%20tank%20of%20the%20American%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20Relations%2C%20Hamas%20and%20Islamic%20Jihad%20want%20to%20stop%20the%20normalisation%20of%20relations%20between%20Israel%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20launched%20the%20October%207%20terrorist%20attacks.%20This%20may%20be%20true%20but%20they%20may%20have%20also%20signed%20their%20own%20death%20warrants%20as%20well%20as%20those%20of%20thousands%20more%20Palestinians.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20can%20Indians%20behave%20this%20way%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPradip%20Biswas%20writes%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20feel%20afresh%2C%20that%20cricket%20matches%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20nothing%20but%20a%20way%20to%20spark%20wild%20frenzy%20which%20could%20end%20up%20in%20communal%20clashes.%20The%20way%20our%20idiot%20boxes%20play%20the%20occasion%20in%20order%20to%20raise%20hate%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community%20is%20a%20direct%20fallout%20of%20the%20fundamentalism%20being%20practised%20by%20the%20RSS%20and%20BJP.%20This%20vexes%20me%20to%20the%20bone.%20If%20a%20cricket%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20sparks%20such%20mental%20%E2%80%98fury%E2%80%99%2C%20nothing%20can%20be%20more%20inhuman.%20When%20such%20ghastly%20scenes%20are%20beamed%20all%20over%20the%20country%20for%20a%20game%2C%20a%20sport%2C%20what%20can%20one%20say%3F%20We%20boast%20of%20being%20a%20federal%20democracy%20but%20what%20is%20shown%20is%20the%20barbarian%20psychology%20of%20our%20people%20at%20its%20worst.%20I%20lose%20hope.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EWrite%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eombudsperson%40thewire.in.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698477629000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F08162927%2FScreenshot-2022-06-08-at-4.29.23-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fbackstory-what-was-the-indian-media-doing-when-a-genocide-was-playing-out-in-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fortnightly%20column%20from%20The%20Wire's%20ombudsperson.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%