E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fus-vetoes-draft-resolution-calling-for-humanitarian-pauses-for-aid-to-gaza%5C%22%3EOn%20October%2018%2C%20the%20United%20States%20vetoed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20a%20draft%20resolution%20tabled%20by%20Brazil%20and%20the%20UAE%20in%20the%20Security%20Council%2C%20which%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Chumanitarian%20pause%E2%80%9D.%20A%20Russian%20draft%20had%20already%20failed%20to%20get%20the%20requisite%20number%20of%20nine%20votes%20to%20be%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20scenario%20unfolded%20a%20week%20later%20on%20Oct%2025%20when%20China%20and%20Russia%20vetoed%20a%20US-led%20draft%20resolution.%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20second%20attempt%20to%20secure%20the%20adoption%20of%20a%20resolution%20also%20fell%20short%20of%20the%20necessary%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20in%20the%20West%20Asian%20region%20escalated%20when%20Hamas%20launched%20an%20incursion%20from%20Gaza%20into%20southern%20Israel%2C%20resulting%20in%20over%201200%20casualties%2C%20including%20hundreds%20of%20civilians.%20Apart%20from%20capturing%20an%20unspecified%20number%20of%20Israeli%20soldiers%2C%20Hamas%20also%20abducted%20more%20than%20220%20Israeli%20and%20foreign%20nationals%20and%20took%20them%20back%20into%20Gaza%20%E2%80%93%20a%20violation%20of%20international%20humantarian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20Israel%20has%20been%20conducting%20extensive%20airstrikes%20in%20Gaza%2C%20leading%20to%207%2C326%20casualties%20(as%20of%20October%2027)%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry.%20Israel%20has%20also%20imposed%20a%20blockade%20on%20the%20supply%20of%20food%2C%20fuel%2C%20electricity%2C%20medical%20supplies%20and%20water%2C%20with%20only%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20food%20and%20medical%20aid%20reaching%20Gaza%20through%20a%20small%20number%20of%20trucks%20allowed%20in%20via%20the%20Rafah%20crossing%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20first%20response%20to%20the%20violence%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20tweet%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Csolidarity%E2%80%9D%20with%20Israel%20on%20October%207.%20This%20was%20further%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-reiterates-solidarity-phone-call-netanyahu-israel-hamas%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereiterated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Modi%20in%20a%20phone%20call%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20a%20week%20later%2C%20he%20spoke%20with%20Palestinian%20President%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-palestine-authority-president-mahmoud-abbas-call-israel-gaza%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMahmoud%20Abbas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20devastating%20explosion%20at%20the%20Al-Ahli%20Baptist%20Hospital%20in%20Gaza.%20India%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20reiterate%20its%20traditional%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20and%20the%20two-state%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20400%20civilians%20were%20killed%2C%20according%20to%20Palestinian%20health%20authorities.%20Israel%20has%20denied%20bombing%20the%20hospital%20but%20the%20video%20evidence%20it%20proffered%20to%20back%20its%20claim%20that%20the%20deadly%20explosion%20at%20Al-Ahli%20was%20the%20result%20of%20a%20misfired%20Palestinian%20rocket%20has%20been%20debunked%20by%20digital%20forensics%20and%20technical%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Modi%20had%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-hamas-war-modi-speaks-with-jordans-king-abdullah-calls-for-early-resolution-of-crisis%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EJordan%E2%80%99s%20King%20Abdullah%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20India%20referred%20to%20the%20need%20for%20an%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20solution%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20humanitarian%20and%20security%20situation.%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20developing%20countries%20that%20has%20not%20called%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Cceasefire%E2%80%9D%20or%20any%20halt%20to%20hostilities%20in%20the%20volatile%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20the%20vote%2C%20Jordan%E2%80%99s%20permanent%20representative%20to%20the%20UN%20Mahmoud%20Daifallah%20Hamoud%20described%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20amendment%20to%20the%20draft%20resolution%20that%20addressed%20a%20humanitarian%20situation%2C%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20perpetrate%20%E2%80%9Cwhitewashing%E2%80%9D%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20atrocities%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20He%20reminded%20the%20UNGA%20that%20they%20were%20%E2%80%9Cwitnessing%20a%20ground%20invasion%20by%20Israel%20as%20we%20speak%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaming%20Hamas%20and%20Israel%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20permanent%20representative%20Bob%20Rae%20contended%20that%20naming%20Hamas%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cfair%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cfactual%E2%80%9D%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20amendment%20%E2%80%9Cnames%20what%20has%20to%20be%20named%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20envoy%20Munir%20Akram%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Canadian%20amendment%20should%20also%20name%20Israel%20as%20well%20for%20the%20retaliatory%20airstrikes.%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20needs%20to%20be%20named%20too%2C%20if%20you%20are%20to%20be%20fair%20and%20equitable%20and%20just%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20Akram%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20better%20not%20to%20name%20any%20sides%20in%20a%20resolution%20that%20was%20just%20calling%20attention%20to%20the%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20ambassador%20Gilad%20Erdan%20said%20that%20the%20UN%20hold%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20even%20one%20ounce%20of%20legitimacy%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20way%20to%20destroy%20Hamas%20is%20to%20root%20them%20out.%20Why%20are%20you%20not%20holding%20Hamas%20accountable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20envoy%20disputed%20statistics%20about%20casualties%20in%20Gaza%2C%20claiming%20that%20Hamas%20was%20propping%20up%20the%20numbers.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20know%20there%20is%20no%20humanitarian%20crisis%20in%20accordance%20with%20international%20humanitarian%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20has%20also%20questioned%20the%20extent%20of%20civilian%20casualties%20in%20Gaza%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F27%2Fun-says-gaza-health-ministry-death-tolls-in-previous-wars%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUN%20has%20vouched%20for%20the%20credibility%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20death%20toll%20the%20Palestinian%20side%20has%20reported%20from%20Gaza%20in%20the%20past.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20health%20ministry%20in%20Gaza%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F26%2Fworld%2Fmiddleeast%2Fgaza-death-toll-israel.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublished%20the%20names%20and%20details%20of%206%2C747%20Palestinians%20killed%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20started%20on%20October%207.%20The%20number%20of%20children%20killed%20was%202%2C655.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUNGA%20resolution%20condemned%20%E2%80%98terrorism%20and%20indiscriminate%20attacks%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETitled%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Funispal%2Fdocument%2Fgeneral-assembly-10ess-draft-resolutioni-l25%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CProtection%20of%20civilians%20and%20upholding%20legal%20and%20humanitarian%20obligations%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20UNGA%20resolution%20condemned%20%E2%80%9Call%20acts%20of%20violence%20against%20Palestinian%20and%20Israeli%20civilians%20including%20all%20acts%20of%20terrorism%20and%20indiscriminate%20attacks%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%C2%A0all%20parties%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20and%20fully%20comply%E2%80%9D%20with%20obligations%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20and%20human%20rights%20laws%2C%20%E2%80%9Cparticularly%20in%20regard%20to%20the%20protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20objects.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20urged%20the%20protection%20of%20humanitarian%20personnel%2C%20the%20wounded%2C%20and%20humanitarian%20facilities%20and%20assets%2C%20and%20to%20enable%20and%20facilitate%20humanitarian%20access%20for%20essential%20supplies%20and%20services%20to%20reach%20all%20civilians%20in%20need%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20resolution%20called%20for%20rescinding%20of%20the%20order%20by%20Israel%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20occupying%20Power%E2%80%9D%2C%20for%20Palestinian%20civilians%2C%20UN%20staff%20and%20humanitarian%20workers%20to%20evacuate%20all%20areas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20north%20of%20Wadi%20Gaza%20and%20relocate%20to%20the%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Release%20all%20civilians%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20General%20Assembly%20also%20called%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20and%20unconditional%20release%E2%80%9D%20of%20all%20civilians%20being%20illegally%20held%20captive%2C%20demanding%20their%20safety%2C%20well-being%20and%20humane%20treatment%20in%20compliance%20with%20international%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20reaffirmed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20and%20lasting%20solution%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%20can%20only%20be%20achieved%20by%20peaceful%20means%2C%20based%20on%20the%20relevant%20UN%20resolutions%20and%20in%20accordance%20with%20international%20law%2C%20and%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20two-state%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20in%20its%20explanation%20of%20vote%2C%20also%20reiterated%20its%20support%20for%20a%20negotiated%20solution%20to%20the%20problem%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20has%20always%20supported%20a%20negotiated%20Two-State%20solution%20to%20the%20Israel-Palestine%20issue%20leading%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20sovereign%2C%20independent%20and%20viable%20State%20of%20Palestine%20living%20within%20secure%20and%20recognized%20borders%2C%20side-by-side%20in%20peace%20with%20Israel.%20For%20this%2C%20we%20urge%20the%20parties%20to%20de-escalate%2C%20eschew%20violence%20and%20work%20towards%20creating%20conditions%20for%20an%20early%20resumption%20of%20direct%20peace%20negotiations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20news.un.org)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698450199000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28045002%2Fy2H-NH7U.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20resolution%20also%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20adhering%20to%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20and%20urged%20the%20unconditional%20release%20of%20all%20captive%20civilians%20as%20well%20as%20the%20unhindered%20supply%20of%20essential%20provisions%20to%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A119%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Going%20undercover%20to%20reveal%20people%20smugglers'%20sales%20tactics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698449596000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F115E7%2Fproduction%2F_131534117_gettyimages-1204298375.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-66984050%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20say%20their%20routes%20from%20Pakistan%20are%20%E2%80%9Csafe%E2%80%9D%2C%20with%20one%20claiming%20%E2%80%9Chundreds%E2%80%9D%20are%20transported%20daily.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%