yalist%20Movement%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27202418%2FThe-Wire-58.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Poet%20and%20novelist%20Malay%20Roychoudhury%2C%20one%20of%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20best-known%20counterculture%20icons%2C%20breathed%20his%20last%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Thursday%2C%20October%2027.%20He%20was%2084.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20co-founder%20of%20the%20Hungry%20Generation%20aka%20Hungryalist%20movement%2C%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20major%20anti-establishment%20literary%20ventures%2C%20Roychoudhury%20was%20one%20of%20Independent%20India%E2%80%99s%20earliest%20poets%20to%20have%20faced%20arrest%20and%20undergone%20trial%20on%20obscenity%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20curses%20that%20Malay%20and%20his%20friends%20spewed%20in%20their%20times%20feel%20like%20gold%20letterings%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20writer%2C%20film%2C%20and%20literature%20critic%20Sanjoy%20Mukhopadhyay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunched%20by%20Bengali%20writers%20in%20the%20early%201960s%2C%20Hungryalist%20literature%20triggered%20nationwide%20debate%20and%20influenced%20anti-establishment%20literary%20movements%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Telugu%2C%20and%20Marathi%20during%20the%20late%20%E2%80%9860s.%20His%20writings%20have%20been%20translated%20into%20several%20major%20Indian%20languages%20as%20well%20as%20English%2C%20German%2C%20French%2C%20Spanish%2C%20Russian%2C%20and%20Italian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%201939%2C%20Roychoudhury%20was%20deeply%20influenced%20by%20the%20slum%20culture%20of%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Imlitala%20ghetto%20where%20he%20and%20his%20elder%20brother%2C%20Samir%2C%20grew%20up.%20Living%20in%20a%20neighbourhood%20comprising%20%E2%80%98low%20caste%E2%80%99%20Hindus%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20Shia%20Muslims%2C%20Roychoudhury%20developed%20his%20literary%20vocabulary%20by%20listening%20to%20his%20neighbour%20reciting%20Ghalib%20and%20Faiz%20Ahmed%20Faiz.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20at%20Ram%20Mohun%20Seminary%20School%2C%20a%20student-cum-librarian%20initiated%20him%20into%20Marxism%20and%20the%20works%20of%20literary%20stalwarts%20like%20Rabindranath%20Tagore%20and%20Jibananda%20Das.%20Two%20servants%20at%20their%20Imlitala%20house%20who%20were%20well%20versed%20in%20poet%20Tulsidasa%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ERamcharitmanas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3ERamshalaka%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20also%20responsible%20for%20moulding%20Roychoudhury%E2%80%99s%20artistic%20sensibilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoychoudhury%20reminisced%20about%20his%20days%20at%20Imlitala%2C%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20photography%20studio%2C%20and%20life%20among%20the%20downtrodden%20in%20%3Cem%3EChotoloker%20Chotobela%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20memoir%20published%20by%20Charchapada%20in%202012.%20%3Cem%3EChhotolok%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20antonym%20for%20%3Cem%3EBhadrolok%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20nomenclature%20used%20to%20describe%20the%20upper-caste%2C%20English-educated%20Bengali%20Hindus.%20Roychoudhury%20always%20insisted%20that%20he%20belonged%20to%20the%20domain%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Echhotolok%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20the%20subaltern.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoychoudhury%E2%80%99s%20father%20had%20sent%20him%20away%20to%20their%20house%20in%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Dariapur%20locality%20and%20the%20older%20brother%20Samir%20to%20Chaibasa%20(now%20in%20Jharkhand)%20so%20that%20they%20would%20escape%20Imlitala%E2%80%99s%20bad%20reputation%20of%20free%20sex%2C%20toddy%2C%20cannabis%2C%20and%20hashish.%20However%2C%20building%20a%20voice%20for%20the%20lowest%20of%20the%20low%20became%20Roychoudhury%E2%80%99s%20passion%20when%20the%20two%20brothers%20were%20confronted%20with%20the%20post-Partition%20upheaval%2C%20sectarian%20violence%2C%20and%20refugee%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Roychoudhury%20said%20in%20a%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcitylights.com%2Finterview-with-malay-roychoudhury-poet-of-hungryalism%2F%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Evan%20Kennedy%20for%20the%20New%20York-based%20City%20Lights%20Bookstore%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%C2%A0told%20my%20brother%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20raise%20our%20voice.%20We%20simple%20people%20have%20nothing%20to%20do.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20print%20leaflets%20against%20the%20government%2C%20the%20system.%20Whatever%20we%20like%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20write%2C%20freely.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20turbulent%201960s%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20humble%20beginnings%2C%20the%20Hungryalist%20movement%20gathered%20momentum%20when%20like-minded%20litterateurs%20like%20Shaileswar%20Ghosh%2C%20Debi%20Roy%2C%20Pradip%20Chaudhuri%2C%20Basudeb%20Dasgupta%2C%20Subhas%20Ghosh%2C%20Falguni%20Roy%2C%20and%20others%20contributed%20to%20the%20vision%20and%20created%20a%20unique%20language%20of%20insult%20and%20anger%20against%20the%20establishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hungryalists%20wanted%20to%20write%20differently%20and%20create%20a%20language%20of%20the%20subaltern.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20different%20authorities%2C%20we%20had%20sent%20paper%20masks%20of%20Indian%20gods%2C%20jokers%2C%20Mickey%20Mouse%2C%20rakshasas.%20They%20were%20really%20cheap%20and%20for%20children.%20On%20the%20reverse%20we%20had%20printed%2C%20%E2%80%98Please%20remove%20your%20mask.%20From%20Hungry%20Generation.%E2%80%99%20They%20never%20thought%20that%20these%20things%20could%20come%20to%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roychoudhury%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27202146%2Fthe-hungries.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22718%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27202146%2Fthe-hungries.jpg%20718w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27202146%2Fthe-hungries-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682153%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22479%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EWriters%20of%20Hungry%20generation.%20From%20the%20top%20left%20moving%20clockwise%3A%20Saileswar%20Ghose%2C%20Malay%20Roy%20Choudhury%20and%20Subhas%20Ghose%20Basudeb%20Dasgupta%2C%20David%20Garcia%2C%20and%20Subimal%20Basak.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FTridib%20Mitra%2FCC%20BY-SA%203.0%20DEED.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20began%20to%20attract%20attention%20and%20create%20controversies%20from%201963%20onwards%20due%20to%20its%20ruthless%20verbiage.%20Allen%20Ginsberg%2C%20one%20of%20the%20pivotal%20figures%20of%20the%20American%20Beat%20Movement%2C%20stayed%20with%20the%20Roychoudhury%20brothers%20in%20Patna%20in%201963.%20Apart%20from%20exchanging%20literary%20notes%2C%20Ginsberg%20also%20took%20photos%20of%20Indian%20lepers%2C%20beggars%2C%20and%20refugees%2C%20which%20angered%20the%20poet%20and%20his%20father.%20Roychoudhury%20thought%20Ginsberg%20was%20seeing%20India%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20a%20common%20white%20tourist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Ginsberg%E2%80%99s%20departure%2C%20Roychoudhury%E2%80%99s%20dangerous%20writings%20were%20to%20change%20his%20life%20unalterably.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20his%201963%20poem%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CPrachanda%20Baidyutik%20Chhutar%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Stark%20Electric%20Jesus)%2C%20which%20prompted%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20against%20the%20Hungryalists.%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOh%20I%E2%80%99ll%20die%20I%E2%80%99ll%20die%20I%E2%80%99ll%20die%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EMy%20skin%20is%20in%20blazing%20furor%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EI%20do%20not%20know%20what%20I%E2%80%99ll%20do%20where%20I%E2%80%99ll%20go%20oh%20I%20am%20sick%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EI%E2%80%99ll%20kick%20all%20the%20Arts%20in%20the%20back%20and%20go%20away%20Shubha%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EShubha%20let%20me%20go%20and%20live%20in%20your%20cloaked%20melon%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20the%20unfastened%20shadow%20of%20dark%20destroyed%20saffron%20curtain%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20last%20anchor%20is%20leaving%20me%20after%20I%20got%20the%20other%20anchors%20lifted%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EI%20can%E2%80%99t%20resist%20anymore%2C%20million%20glass-panes%20are%20breaking%20in%20my%20cortex%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EI%20know%2C%20Shubha%2C%20spread%20out%20your%20matrix%2C%20give%20me%20peace%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EEach%20vein%20is%20carrying%20a%20stream%20of%20tears%20up%20to%20the%20heart%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EBrain%E2%80%99s%20contagious%20flints%20are%20decomposing%20out%20of%20eternal%20sickness%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EMother%20why%20didn%E2%80%99t%20you%20give%20me%20birth%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20skeleton%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EI%E2%80%99d%20have%20gone%20two%20billion%20light%20years%20and%20kissed%20God%E2%80%99s%20ass%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EBut%20nothing%20pleases%20me%20nothing%20sounds%20well%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EI%20feel%20nauseated%20with%20more%20than%20a%20single%20kiss%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EI%E2%80%99ve%20forgotten%20women%20during%20copulation%20and%20returned%20to%20Muse%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EInto%20the%20sun-colored%20bladder%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EI%20do%20not%20know%20what%20these%20happenings%20are%20but%20they%20are%20occurring%20within%20me%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(An%20excerpt%20from%20Malay%20Roychoudhury%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9CStark%20Electric%20Jesus%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20published%20in%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3ECity%20Lights%3Cem%3E%20Journal%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ENumber%203%20(1966))%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20first%20Hungry%20anthology%20came%20out%20in%20March%201964%2C%20police%20picked%20up%20six%20of%20them%20in%20a%20string%20of%20arrests%20%E2%80%93%20Saileshwar%20Ghosh%20and%20Subhas%20Ghosh%20from%20Kolkata%3B%20Malay%20and%20Samir%20Roychoudhury%20from%20Patna%3B%20Pradip%20Choudhuri%20from%20Tripura%3B%20and%20Haradhan%20Dhara%20from%20Howrah.%20Malay%20alone%20underwent%20trial%20for%20%E2%80%98obscenity%E2%80%99%20in%20his%20poem%2C%20as%20the%20police%20tried%20to%20turn%20the%20other%20accused%20into%20approvers%20against%20him.%20However%2C%20most%20of%20these%20poets%20ultimately%20defended%20him%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20city%20sessions%20court%20in%20Kolkata%20convicted%20Roychoudhury%2C%20he%20was%20later%20acquitted%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court.%20The%20entire%20legal%20battle%20lasted%20nearly%20three%20years.%20The%20chain%20of%20events%20took%20Kolkata%E2%80%99s%20literary%20sphere%20by%20storm.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3ETime%20Magazine%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereported%20on%20the%20trial%20in%20their%20November%201964%20issue%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20land%20that%20has%20become%20so%20straitly%20laced%20that%20its%20movie%20heroines%20must%20burst%20into%20song%20rather%20than%20be%20kissed%2C%20five%20scruffy%20young%20poets%20were%20hauled%20into%20Calcutta%E2%80%99s%20dreary%20Bankshall%20Court%20for%20publishing%20works%20that%20would%20have%20melted%20even%20Vatsyayana%E2%80%99s%20pen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%201970%2C%20translations%20of%20Hungryalist%20texts%20appeared%20in%20literary%20periodicals%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20Mexico%2C%20Argentina%2C%20Australia%2C%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20the%20US.%20Close%20to%2060%20Hungry-influenced%20magazines%20were%20published%20between%20the%201960s%20and%20%E2%80%9980s%2C%20including%20%3Cem%3EKshudhartha%20Pratirodh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20Hungry%20Resistance)%2C%20%3Cem%3ESwakal%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Our%20Times)%2C%20%3Cem%3EPphoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Huh!)%2C%20%3Cem%3EUpadruta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Disturbed)%2C%20%3Cem%3EZebra%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EGiraffe%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%201965%2C%20the%20movement%20fizzled%20out%2C%20beaten%20out%20of%20shape%20and%20spirit%20by%20the%20authority%E2%80%99s%20harsh%20measures.%20For%20a%20time%2C%20Roychoudhury%20took%20up%20a%20government%20job%20at%20Agriculture%2C%20Refinance%2C%20and%20Development%20Corporation.%20On%20his%20return%20to%20literary%20life%20two%20decades%20later%2C%20he%20won%20and%20declined%20the%20Sahitya%20Academic%20Award%20for%20translating%20Dharamvir%20Bharati%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3ESuraj%20Ka%20Satwan%20Ghora%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20Bengali.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%201995%2C%20Roychoudhury%E2%80%99s%20literary%20career%20took%20a%20dramatic%20turn%20as%20he%20introduced%20his%20%3Cem%3EAdhunantika%20%3C%2Fem%3Ephase%20(%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EAdhu%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3Emeaning%20%E2%80%9Cnew%E2%80%9D%3B%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ENantik%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3Emeaning%20%E2%80%98end%E2%80%99)%20where%20he%20became%20one%20of%20Bengali%20literature%E2%80%99s%20pioneering%20voices%20in%20the%20post-modernist%20writing%20style.%20His%20poetry%20collections%20from%20this%20phase%20are%C2%A0%3Cem%3EChitkar%20Samagra%2C%20Chhatrakhan%2C%20Ja%20Lagbey%20Bolben%2C%20Atmadhangser%20Sahasrabda%2C%20Postmodern%20Ahlader%20Kobita%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKounaper%20Luchimangso%3C%2Fem%3E.%20His%20novels%20from%20the%20period%20include%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENamgandho%2C%20Jalanjali%2C%20Nakhadanta%2C%20Ei%20Adham%20Oi%20Adham%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EArup%20Tomar%20Entokanta%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20lines%20from%20%3Cem%3EBlood%20Lyric%20%3C%2Fem%3Epublished%20in%202011%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20have%20I%20done%20for%20poetry%20plunging%20into%C2%A0%20lava-spewing%20volcano%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cbr%3E%20What%20are%20these%3F%20What%20are%20these%3F%20Result%20of%20searches%20at%20home%3Cbr%3E%20of%20Poetry%3F%20Bromide%20sepia%20babies%20from%20Dad%E2%80%99s%20broken%20almirah%3Cbr%3E%20of%20Poetry!%20Mom%E2%80%99s%20Benares%20sari%20torn%20out%20of%20hammered%20box%3Cbr%3E%20of%20Poetry!%20Breaths%20are%20recorded%20in%20the%20seizure%20list%3Cbr%3E%20of%20Poetry!%20Show%20me%20show%20me%20what%20else%20is%20coming%20out%3Cbr%3E%20of%20Poetry!%20Shame%20on%20you%3B%20girl%E2%80%99s%20half-licked%20guy!%20Die%20you%20die%3Cbr%3E%20of%20Poetry!%20Wave%20piercing%20sharks%20chew%20up%20flesh%20%26amp%3B%20bone%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERoychoudhury%20continued%20to%20be%20active%20on%20the%20Bengali%20literary%20circuit%2C%20with%20books%20and%20writings%20being%20released%20regularly%20in%20the%20Kolkata%20Book%20Fair%20and%20the%20Little%20Magazine%20Fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20news%20of%20his%20death%20broke%2C%20the%20little%20magazine%20fraternity%20of%20Bengal%2C%20India%2C%20and%20abroad%20took%20to%20social%20media%20in%20hoards%20to%20express%20their%20condolences.%20Many%20lamented%20his%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20impact%20and%20influence%20over%20India%E2%80%99s%20counter-establishment%20scenario%20were%20beautifully%20summed%20up%20by%20the%20late%20American%20writer-scholar%20Howard%20McCord%3A%20%E2%80%9CMalay%20Roy%20Choudhury%2C%20a%20Bengali%20poet%2C%20has%20been%20a%20central%20figure%20in%20the%20Hungry%20Generation%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20the%20Indian%20cultural%20establishment%20since%20the%20movement%20began%20in%20the%20early%201960s.%20%E2%80%A6Acid%2C%20destructive%2C%20morbid%2C%20nihilistic%2C%20outrageous%2C%20mad%2C%20hallucinatory%2C%20shrill%20%E2%80%93%20these%20characterise%20the%20terrifying%20and%20cleansing%20visions%E2%80%9D%20that%20%E2%80%9CIndian%20literature%20must%20endure%20if%20it%20is%20to%20be%20vital%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalay%20Roychoudhury%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%20Shalila%20Roychoudhury%2C%20his%20daughter%20Anushree%20Prashant%2C%20son%20Jitendra%20and%20two%20grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESreemanti%20Sengupta%20is%20a%20Kolkata-based%20freelance%20writer%2C%20poet%2C%20and%20media%20studies%20lecturer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698418721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27202418%2FThe-Wire-58.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fmalay-roychoudhury-1939-2023-the-explosive-poet-of-indias-hungryalist-movement%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Malay%20Roychoudhury%2C%20one%20of%20the%20co-founders%20of%20the%201960s'%20Hungryalist%20literary%20movement%2C%20was%20a%20notorious%20cocktail%20of%20confessional%20verse%20that%20continually%20flouted%20norms%20and%20flirted%20with%20danger.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fmalay-roychoudhury-1939-2023-the-explosive-poet-of-indias-hungryalist-movement%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paytm%20subsidiary%20inks%20pact%20with%20Startup%20Bihar%20to%20offer%20banking%20solutions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698417428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-11%2F25%2Ffull%2F1637817326-8086.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpaytm-subsidiary-inks-pact-with-startup-bihar-to-offer-banking-solutions-123102701015_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Startup%20Bihar%20is%20the%20state%20government's%20ambitious%20initiative%20to%20promote%20startups%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpaytm-subsidiary-inks-pact-with-startup-bihar-to-offer-banking-solutions-123102701015_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpaytm-subsidiary-inks-pact-with-startup-bihar-to-offer-banking-solutions-123102701015_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpaytm-subsidiary-inks-pact-with-startup-bihar-to-offer-banking-solutions-123102701015_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SJVN%20Green%20collaborates%20with%20Ocean%20Sun%20for%20new%20tech%20in%20green%2C%20clean%20energy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698417245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-03%2F27%2Ffull%2F1679918112-5954.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsjvn-green-collaborates-with-ocean-sun-for-new-tech-in-green-clean-energy-123102700984_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20MoU%20shall%20pave%20way%20for%20technology%20transfer%20and%20cooperation%20amongst%20the%20two%20countries%2C%20it%20added%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsjvn-green-collaborates-with-ocean-sun-for-new-tech-in-green-clean-energy-123102700984_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsjvn-green-collaborates-with-ocean-sun-for-new-tech-in-green-clean-energy-123102700984_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsjvn-green-collaborates-with-ocean-sun-for-new-tech-in-green-clean-energy-123102700984_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Telangana%3A%20What%20Explains%20the%20Decline%20of%20BRS%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170220%2FF9XxRh3aQAA_Hcy.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%2C%20formerly%20Telangana%20Rashtra%20Samithi%2C%20is%20witnessing%20an%20unprecedented%20decline.%20Going%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F201023%2Fsurvey-shows-congress-surge-in-telangana.html%5C%22%3Erecent%20surveys%3C%2Fa%3E%20ahead%20of%20the%20November%2030%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Congress%20is%20clearly%20on%20the%20ascendancy%20while%20the%20BRS%20is%20losing%20ground.%20Even%20if%20these%20surveys%20turn%20out%20modestly%20right%20and%20the%20BRS%20footprint%20declines%2C%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at%20the%20reasons%20closely%20not%20only%20to%20understand%20the%20developments%20in%20Telangana%20but%20also%20to%20make%20sense%20of%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20general%20election%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelangana%20was%20formed%20in%202014%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20at%20the%20Centre.%20BRS%20won%20the%20first%20and%20second%20assembly%20elections%20held%20in%20the%20new%20state%20due%20to%20the%20expansive%20transactional%20welfarism%20it%20rolled%20out%2C%20regional%20sentiment%2C%20relief%20from%20extreme%20drought%20conditions%20due%20to%20the%20digging%20of%20ponds%2C%20and%20laying%20new%20pipelines%20for%20the%20supply%20of%20drinking%20water.%20Further%2C%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20(KCR)%20maintained%20a%20fair%20degree%20of%20communal%20harmony%20with%20special%20funds%20for%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20appointing%20a%20Muslim%20leader%20as%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20pitching%20for%2012%25%20reservations%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-brs-kcr-congress-bjp%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Polls%3A%20BRS%20Has%20Reason%20Not%20To%20Be%20Overconfident%20With%20Congress%20Poised%20To%20Challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20brought%20in%20the%20unique%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme%20for%20landowning%20farmers%20by%20granting%20Rs%205%2C000%20per%20acre%20twice%20a%20year%20in%20the%20form%20of%20investment%20support%20for%20agriculture.%20His%20government%20also%20announced%20the%20Dalit%20Bandhu%20scheme%2C%20which%20promised%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Dalit%20families%20to%20help%20set%20up%20their%20own%20business%20ventures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20government%20has%20also%20started%20a%20Telangana%20Brahmin%20Samkshema%20Parishad%20to%20offer%20educational%20loans%20and%20support%20to%20Brahmin%20students%20who%20wish%20to%20pursue%20their%20higher%20education%20abroad.%20Since%20Telangana%20began%20as%20a%20state%20with%20a%20surplus%20budget%20in%202014%2C%20KCR%20rightly%20focused%20on%20welfare%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20bring%20about%20relief%20to%20most%20sections%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20faced%20neglect%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Andhra%20capitalists%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20united%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoss%20of%20direction%20in%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20second%20term%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20problems%20of%20misgovernance%20and%20a%20loss%20of%20direction%20have%20marked%20the%20second%20term%20of%20chief%20minister%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20(2018-present).%20Though%20his%20government%20still%20continues%20with%20many%20of%20its%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20visible%20change%20of%20mood%20in%20the%20state.%20Known%20for%20its%20social%20protest%20movements%2C%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20demography%20is%20dominated%20by%20Dalits%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20and%20Muslims.%20Together%2C%20these%20groups%20constitute%2085%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%20It%20was%20movements%20led%20by%20each%20of%20these%20groups%20and%20their%20demands%20that%20gathered%20strength%20to%20culminate%20in%20articulating%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20state%20of%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20delivered%20on%20transactional%20welfarism%2C%20but%20also%20stoically%20neglected%20the%20aspirational%20demands%20rooted%20in%20the%20statehood%20movement%20such%20as%20%E2%80%98KG%20to%20PG%E2%80%99%20free%20education.%20He%20neglected%20higher%20education%20as%20he%20was%20upset%20over%20youth%20being%20part%20of%20many%20of%20the%20social%20mobilisations%20in%20the%20state.%20Universities%20in%20the%20state%20functioned%20without%20vice-chancellors%20for%20well%20over%20three%20years%20after%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%20in%202014.%20Many%20of%20these%20universities%20still%20continue%20to%20starve%20for%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENeglect%20of%20education%20has%20been%20coupled%20with%20the%20encouragement%20received%20by%20caste-based%20occupations%20through%20funds%20specifically%20given%20towards%20their%20modernisation.%20This%20presented%20a%20rather%20grim%20picture%20for%20the%20future%20of%20many%20Dalit-Bahujan%20castes.%20The%20BRS%20presented%20subsistence%20welfare%20but%20failed%20to%20fulfil%20aspirational%20imagination.%20The%20decline%20of%20BRS%20marks%20the%20shift%20from%20subsistence%20relief%20provided%20by%20patronage%20politics%20to%20aspirational%20politics%20based%20on%20self-respect%20and%20greater%20social%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20narrow%20and%20casteist%20vision%20of%20KCR%20is%20best%20represented%20in%20his%20own%20persona%2C%20which%20is%20abrasive%2C%20arrogant%2C%20and%20non-responsive.%20He%20emerged%20on%20the%20political%20scene%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20protest%2C%20but%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20manifested%20nothing%20but%20contempt%20for%20mass%20mobilisations.%20He%20also%20distanced%20himself%20from%20mass%20leaders%20of%20the%20statehood%20movement%20and%20got%20many%20of%20them%20arrested%2C%20including%20Kodandaram%2C%20who%20is%20now%20the%20chief%20of%20Telangana%20Jana%20Samithi.%20Recently%2C%20a%20case%20was%20framed%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Factivists-haragopal-sudha-bharadwaj-150-others-booked-under-uapa-last-august-accused-unaware%5C%22%3Ewell-known%20activists%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20protests%20from%20various%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20popular%20anecdote%20among%20civil%20society%20activists%20in%20the%20state%20is%20that%20KCR%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20famous%20balladeer%20Gaddar%2C%20who%20waited%20for%20hours%20for%20an%20appointment.%20It%20is%20this%20arrogance%20of%20KCR%20that%20culminated%20in%20undermining%20the%20very%20regional%20sentiments%20that%20brought%20him%20to%20power.%20His%20aspiration%20to%20take%20his%20party%20national%20has%20also%20undermined%20legitimate%20regional%20sentiments.%20This%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20suicidal%20as%20there%20has%20been%20a%20loss%20of%20emotional%20connection%20with%20regional%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20failed%20attempts%20to%20emerge%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20BRS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20space%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20attempted%20to%20capture%20in%20Telangana.%20It%20attempted%20to%20communalise%20regional%20imagination.%20This%20did%20not%20work%20in%20Telangana%2C%20though%20it%20continues%20to%20have%20reasonable%20appeal%20among%20caste-Hindu%20middle%20classes.%20The%20BJP%20began%20to%20grow%20with%20great%20appeal%20among%20the%20OBCs.%20It%20then%20attempted%20to%20combine%20social%20justice%20with%20communal%20polarisation.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funion-minister-kishan-reddy-made-telangana-bjp-chief-punjab-jharkhand-get-new-presidents%5C%22%3EBandi%20Sanjay%3C%2Fa%3E%20(who%20is%20from%20the%20OBC%20Munnuru%20Kapu%20community)%2C%20the%20BJP%20expanded%20its%20footprint.%20But%20Telangana%20has%20remained%20the%20land%20of%20Reddy%20domination%2C%20as%20Andhra%20is%20of%20the%20Kammas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F06184339%2FUntitled-design-2022-07-06T184215.792-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-606011%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBJP%20Telangana%20unit%20president%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20BJP%20national%20executive%20meeting%20held%20on%20July%204%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20leadership%20of%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20pursuing%20the%20policy%20of%20undermining%20independent%20leaders%20in%20states%2C%20following%20a%20clue%20from%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20brand%20of%20politics.%20They%20refuse%20to%20learn%20the%20lesson%20in%20a%20pitch%20to%20push%20for%20complete%20dependence%20on%20the%20manufactured%20charisma%20of%20Narendra%20Modi.%20They%20refuse%20to%20learn%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-cracks-appearing-in-bjps-telangana-unit-after-the-karnataka-debacle%5C%22%3Edebacle%20in%20Karnataka%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20undermining%20Yeddyurappa%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20and%20staring%20at%20a%20steep%20challenge%20in%20Rajasthan%20after%20undermining%20the%20leadership%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-bjp-rebellion-first-list-publicly-opposed%5C%22%3EVasundhara%20Raje%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20wants%20to%20expand%20but%20with%20Modi%20as%20its%20only%20popular%20face.%20Beyond%20North%20and%20West%20India%2C%20Modi%20is%20not%20a%20leader%20with%20great%20reach%20in%20the%20South%20and%20the%20East.%20With%20the%20appointment%20of%20Union%20minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Funion-minister-kishan-reddy-made-telangana-bjp-chief-punjab-jharkhand-get-new-presidents%5C%22%3EKishan%20Reddy%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Telangana%20BJP%20unit%20chief%20in%20the%20place%20of%20Bandi%20Sanjay%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20declined%20in%20terms%20of%20popular%20presence.%20Political%20pundits%20who%20were%20at%20one%20point%20predicting%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20BJP%20forming%20a%20government%20give%20them%20no%20more%20than%20five%20seats%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-telangana-polls-brs-kcr-rahul-gandhi%5C%22%3EFrom%20Pushover%20to%20Position%20of%20Strength%3A%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Gain%20Evident%20in%20Public%20Outcry%20Against%20BRS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevival%20of%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20perception%20among%20some%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20BRS%2C%20and%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20are%20working%20in%20tandem%20to%20arrest%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20Congress.%20This%20has%20now%20made%20it%20a%20bipolar%20contest%20between%20Congress%20and%20the%20rest.%20The%20Congress%20has%20begun%20to%20articulate%20the%20new%20demands%20and%20regional%20aspirations%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20recent%20announcement%20that%20Kodandaram%2C%20a%20key%20leader%20of%20the%20statehood%20movement%20and%20the%20Telangana%20Jana%20Samithi%20chief%2C%20will%20work%20and%20contest%20together%20with%20the%20Congress%20has%20further%20helped%20the%20party%20capture%20the%20protest%20space%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170909%2FTelangana-Congress.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170909%2FTelangana-Congress.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170909%2FTelangana-Congress-300x207.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170909%2FTelangana-Congress-1024x706.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682103%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22827%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leaders%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%2C%20and%20others%20during%20the%20election%20campaign%20in%20Telangana.%20Photo%3A%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40RahulGandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20replication%20of%20the%20experiment%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20more%20than%20100%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fpolitics%2Fcivil-society-organisations-played-key-role-in-congress-victory%2Farticle66846656.ece%5C%22%3Ecivil%20society%20organisations%3C%2Fa%3E%20worked%20independently%20but%20with%20a%20desire%20to%20keep%20out%20the%20BJP%2C%20in%20Telangana%20too%2C%20over%2050%20organisations%20came%20together%20under%20the%20platform%20of%20Telangana%20Vidhyavanthula%20Vedika%20to%20campaign%20independently%20against%20the%20misrule%20of%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20danger%20posed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20These%20organisations%20have%20close%20grassroots%20connections%20in%20various%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKCR%20moved%20from%20being%20the%20poster%20boy%20of%20Telangana%20sensibilities%20and%20identity%20to%20betraying%20and%20undermining%20not%20only%20material%20mobility%20but%20psychological%20and%20emotional%20identification.%20This%20is%20akin%20to%20the%20terminal%20decline%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20when%20it%20turned%20against%20the%20peasants%20who%20were%20its%20mainstay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20increasingly%20occupying%20this%20space%20and%20filling%20the%20void%20both%20because%20of%20the%20favourable%20role%20it%20played%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20separate%20state%20through%20Sonal%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20and%20with%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20presenting%20a%20left-of-centre%20vision.%20This%20shift%20is%20happening%20with%20scepticism%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20return%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Reddy%20landlordism%E2%80%99%20that%20Congress%20represented%20in%20the%20past%20in%20Telangana.%20If%20Congress%20maintains%20its%20transformative%20image%2C%20symbolism%2C%20and%20policy%20frame%2C%20it%20could%20look%20at%20a%20long%20haul%2C%20otherwise%2C%20people%20will%20move%20on%20to%20look%20for%20other%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmigrant-workers-middle-class-lockdown%5C%22%3EAjay%20Gudavarthy%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Political%20Studies%2C%20JNU.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698416945000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27170220%2FF9XxRh3aQAA_Hcy.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-what-explains-the-decline-of-brs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20state%20in%202014%2C%20the%20KCR%20government%20rightly%20focused%20on%20welfare.%20But%20recently%2C%20it%20is%20suffering%20because%20of%20alleged%20misgovernance%20and%20the%20perceived%20arrogance%20of%20KCR.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-what-explains-the-decline-of-brs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Coursemate%20Appeals%3A%20Bring%20Back%20Indian%20Navy%20Veterans%20on%20Death%20Row%20in%20Qatar%20Now%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27184644%2Fmodi-thani.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sudden%2C%20shocking%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20eight%20former%20Indian%20Navy%20officials%20who%20were%20incarcerated%20in%20Qatar%20on%20unknown%20charges%20since%20August%2030%20last%20year%20were%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37210%2FVerdict_in_the_case_of_8_Indians_detained_in_Qatar%5C%22%3Esentenced%20to%20death%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20by%20a%20Qatari%20%E2%80%98Court%20of%20First%20Instance%E2%80%99.%20Families%20of%20the%20eight%20veterans%20who%20held%20on%20to%20a%20sliver%20of%20hope%20that%20back-channel%20efforts%20may%20secure%20their%20release%20now%20face%20the%20most%20extreme%20prospect%20%E2%80%94%20Death%20Row.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20naval%20veterans%20were%20working%20for%20a%20now-defunct%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fthe-story-behind-qatar-sentencing-eight-indian-ex-navy-officers-to-death%2Farticleshow%2F104731250.cms%5C%22%3EDahra%20Global%20Technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Doha.%20Their%20area%20of%20expertise%20was%20training%20and%20assisting%20the%20Qatari%20Emiri%20Forces%20in%20setting%20up%20defence%20capacities%20%E2%80%93%20a%20vital%20cog%20in%20the%20wheel%20of%20Indo-Qatar%20bilateral%20defence%20cooperation%20and%20foreign%20policy.%20One%20of%20the%20wealthiest%20countries%20today%2C%20the%20tiny%20kingdom%20of%20Qatar%20has%20traditionally%20enjoyed%20warm%20and%20cordial%20relations%20with%20India.%20Today%2C%20an%20estimated%20diaspora%20of%20800%2C000%20Indians%2C%20along%20with%20other%20nationalities%2C%20contribute%20to%20building%20this%20country%20in%20various%20capacities%2C%20brick%20by%20brick%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Emir%20Sheikh%20Tamim%20Hamad%20Al%20Thani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20the%20present%20case%20are%20far%20too%20sketchy%20and%20opaque%20to%20justify%20such%20an%20extreme%20sentence%20in%20such%20a%20short%20trial.%20There%20have%20hardly%20been%20three%20hearings%20since%20the%20first%20one%20on%20March%2022%20this%20year.%20Since%20their%20incarceration%20in%20August%202022%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20provided%20the%20veterans%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbest%E2%80%9D%20legal%20assistance.%20It%20is%20unlikely%20that%20substantive%20arguments%20from%20the%20(local)%20defence%20counsel%20would%20be%20heard%20and%20addressed%20in%20just%20three%20hearings%20over%20seven%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Cdeath%20sentence%E2%80%9D%20has%20left%20the%20Indian%20establishment%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20a%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37210%2FVerdict_in_the_case_of_8_Indians_detained_in_Qatar%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20out%20on%20October%2026%2C%20soon%20after%20sentencing.%20The%20MEA%20statement%20indicates%20an%20%E2%80%98unexpected%20outcome%E2%80%99%20while%20also%20hinting%20at%20the%20opacity%20of%20charges%20framed%20against%20the%20officials.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Qatar%20has%20acted%20in%20complete%20secrecy%2C%20moving%20from%20trial%20to%20conviction%20in%20seven%20months.%20Apparently%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20complete%20surprise.%20Often%2C%20when%20expectations%20fall%20woefully%20short%20of%20outcome%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20one%20is%20left%20with%20nothing%20but%20tears.%20I%20know%20this%20from%20personal%20experience.%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20affected%20families%2C%20even%20strangers%20with%20a%20conscience%2C%20had%20a%20lump%20in%20their%20throats%20when%20this%20news%20broke%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16130122%2F006_Al_Udeid.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22850%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16130122%2F006_Al_Udeid.jpg%20850w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16130122%2F006_Al_Udeid-300x125.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-644224%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22355%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E006%20Al%20Udeid%2C%20Qatari%20Emiri%20Navy%20Bazan%20class%20off-shore%20patrol%20boat.%20Representative%20image.%20Photo%3A%20Murgatroyd49%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20episode%20is%20personal%20at%20many%20levels.%20Two%20of%20the%20eight%20%E2%80%93%20Commander%20Sanjeev%20Gupta%20and%20Commander%20Amit%20Nagpal%20%E2%80%93%20are%20my%20coursemates%2C%20whom%20I%20have%20known%20personally%20for%20over%20four%20decades.%20It%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Efauji%3C%2Fem%3E%20truism%20that%20nobody%20%E2%80%93%20not%20even%20your%20spouse%20%E2%80%93%20knows%20you%20better%20than%20a%20coursemate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESanjeev%20(First%20Course%20of%2010%2B2(X)%2C%20%E2%80%9COceans%20Best%E2%80%9D)%2C%20my%20namesake%20and%20one%20of%20the%20convicted%2C%20was%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Chote%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98Don%E2%80%99%20in%20our%20course.%20His%20small%20frame%20hides%20an%20outsized%20heart%20and%20rock-solid%20patriotism%20while%20his%20ever-helpful%20nature%20earned%20him%20the%20latter%20epithet.%20Such%20is%20his%20obsession%20with%20propriety%20and%20fairness%20that%20on%20one%20of%20my%20earliest%20visits%20to%20his%20hometown%20Agra%2C%20he%20dragged%20my%20errant%20auto%20rickshaw%20driver%20all%20the%20way%20from%20the%20bus%20station%20to%20the%20local%20police%20station%20to%20register%20a%20complaint%20for%20charging%20%E2%80%98excess%20to%20meter%E2%80%99.%20His%20peers%20and%20subordinates%20will%20recount%20numerous%20anecdotes%20where%20his%20%3Cem%3Edildaar%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20can-do%20attitude%20saved%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmit%20(78%20NDA)%20or%20%E2%80%98Naggy%E2%80%99%20as%20we%20call%20him%20in%20our%20circles%2C%20is%20a%20quintessential%20gentleman%20%E2%80%93%20a%20man%20of%20few%20words%20and%20impeccable%20character%20whom%20I%20first%20met%20when%20we%20ran%20into%20our%20NDA%20coursemates%20on%20ships%20of%20the%20training%20squadron%20at%20Kochi.%20A%20communication%20and%20electronic%20warfare%20specialist%2C%20he%20knows%20the%20value%20of%20%E2%80%9Cindiscretion%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cradio%20silence%E2%80%9D%20better%20than%20most.%20Always%20professional%2C%20meticulous%20and%20%E2%80%9Cofficer-like%E2%80%9D%20to%20a%20fault%2C%20Naggy%20and%20I%20did%20the%2061st%20staff%20course%20together%20at%20Defence%20Services%20Staff%20College%2C%20Wellington%2C%202005-06.%20I%20cannot%20begin%20to%20fathom%20the%20fate%20that%20befalls%20him%20and%20his%20family%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20can%20sign%20a%20character%20certificate%20for%20these%20two%20officers%20%3Cem%3Ewith%20my%20eyes%20closed%3C%2Fem%3E.%20So%20can%20a%20multitude%20of%20naval%20officials%20who%20have%20known%20or%20worked%20with%20these%20eight%20veterans%2C%20including%20sailor%20Ragesh.%20These%20are%20honest%2C%20above-board%20gentlemen%20who%20worked%20with%20the%20same%20zeal%20and%20commitment%20in%20Indian%20Navy%20service%20as%20in%20their%20selected%20fields%20post-retirement.%20I%20challenge%20those%20who%20know%20them%20personally%20to%20publicly%20reveal%20to%20me%20a%20single%20act%20of%20indiscretion%20that%20even%20remotely%20points%20to%20suspicions%20of%20the%20nature%20they%20have%20allegedly%20been%20charged%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20managing%20director%20of%20their%20enterprise%2C%20Commodore%20Purnendu%20Tiwari%20(I%20do%20not%20know%20him%20personally)%2C%20was%20felicitated%20with%20the%20Pravasi%20Bhartiya%20Samman%20Award%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20at%20a%20glittering%20ceremony%20in%20January%202019%20for%20%E2%80%9Cenhancing%20India%E2%80%99s%20image%20abroad%E2%80%9D.%20Commodore%20Tiwari%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20veteran%20to%20be%20awarded%20this%20honour%20meant%20for%20NRIs%2FPIOs.%20How%20did%20these%20character%20certificates%20suddenly%20dissolve%20into%20a%20death%20sentence%3F%20What%20level%20of%20bungling%20led%20to%20this%20impasse%3F%20Whom%20are%20we%20seeking%20to%20protect%3F%20This%20is%20something%20the%20Indian%20government%20needs%20to%20come%20clean%20about.%20Not%20least%20because%20Qatar%20won%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20quite%20obviously%2C%20missing%20pieces%20to%20this%20puzzle%2C%20yet%20to%20be%20uncovered%20by%20investigative%20noses%20from%20India.%20But%2C%20I%20fear%2C%20under%20a%20climate%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eab%20tum%20chup%20raho%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20nosediving%20indices%20of%20press%20freedom%2C%20facts%20may%20never%20come%20out%2C%20even%20if%20they%20lurk%20beneath%20the%20surface%2C%20or%2C%20worse%20still%2C%20point%20to%20the%20establishment.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Qatar%20has%20proceeded%20unapologetically%2C%20thumbing%20their%20noses%20at%20our%20soft-pedalling%20attitude%20(remember%2C%20our%20VP%20visited%20Qatar%20during%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%20inaugural).%20The%20latest%20judgment%20can%20best%20be%20described%20as%20a%20resounding%20slap%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Indian%20diplomacy.%20Is%20it%20okay%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D%20at%20such%20travesties%20when%20%3Cem%3EVishwaguru%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20the%20image%20that%20is%20unabashedly%20being%20promoted%20by%20all%20arms%20of%20the%20government%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20fear%20this%20case%20may%20go%20the%20Kulbhushan%20Jadhav%20way%20(another%20very%20unfortunate%20case%2C%20the%20trail%20of%20which%20case%20seems%20to%20have%20gone%20cold)%20unless%20we%20move%20with%20alacrity.%20There%20are%20distinct%20differences%2C%20though%20I%20sincerely%20wish%20India%20had%20done%20more%20for%20Kulbhushan%E2%80%99s%20case.%20Dahra%20Global%20and%20its%20verticals%20were%20doing%20above-ground%20work%20in%20a%20crucial%20area%20of%20Indo-Qatar%20defence%20collaboration.%20This%20space%20would%20undoubtedly%20have%20international%20competitors%20with%20enormous%20clout%2C%20money%20and%20political%20patronage%20who%20would%20(undoubtedly)%20gain%20from%20the%20fall%20of%20Dahra%20Global%20and%20the%20scapegoating%20of%20these%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans.%20Perhaps%20it%20is%20time%20for%20the%20public%2C%20if%20not%20the%20government%2C%20to%20seek%20answers%20to%20the%20old%20police%20maxim%3A%20%E2%80%9CWho%20benefits%20from%20the%20crime%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20terrible%20turn%20of%20events%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20come%20at%20a%20more%20inopportune%20moment%20for%20the%20convicted%20veterans%20and%20their%20families.%20Dahra%20Global%20Technologies%20in%20Qatar%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20going%20concern%2C%20which%20means%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20personnel%20are%20pretty%20much%20on%20their%20own.%20India%E2%80%99s%20nuanced%20position%20on%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20and%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%20will%20be%20put%20to%20the%20test%20against%20Qatar%E2%80%99s%20emerging%20role%20in%20working%20out%20a%20rapprochement%20between%20the%20Arab%20world%20and%20Israel%2C%20even%20as%20world%20leaders%20weigh%20their%20options.%20Our%20relationship%20with%20Qatar%20will%20head%20south%20if%20the%20ensuing%20diplomatic%20row%20after%20the%20latest%20imbroglio%20is%20not%20settled%20on%20mutually%20acceptable%20terms.%20India%20is%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20fever%2C%20where%20absurd%20theatrics%20and%20sporting%20fervour%20can%20easily%20eclipse%20real-life%20problems.%20If%20all%20this%20is%20not%20bad%20enough%2C%20India%20is%20headed%20into%20a%20general%20election%20season%20where%20parties%20will%20politicise%20every%20available%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20of%20hypnotising%20billions%20with%20an%20image%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cworld%20leader%E2%80%9D%20or%20Vishwaguru%20is%20that%20sometimes%20problems%20crop%20up%20that%20demand%20the%20full%20agency%20of%20such%20leaders%20to%20step%20in%20and%20solve%20complicated%20problems.%20Now%20the%20unthinkable%20has%20happened%20%E2%80%93%20eight%20Indian%20Navy%20veterans%20are%20on%20death%20row%20in%20a%20friendly%20foreign%20country%20and%20the%20MEA%20under%20our%20strongman%2C%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20is%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20shocked%E2%80%9D.%20Whatever%20that%20means%20in%20diplomacy%2C%20this%20event%20has%20no%20precedence%20in%20modern%20India.%20The%20minions%2C%20influencers%2C%20Ambassadors%20and%20lawyers%20have%20done%20their%20bit%2C%20had%20their%20say.%20No%20more%20passing%20of%20the%20buck%20is%20possible.%20The%20issue%20is%20right%20here%20on%20the%20table%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20ruler%20of%20a%20wealthy%20Middle%20East%20kingdom%20that%20served%20us%2014-month%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBring%20Back%20our%20naval%20veterans%20on%20Death%20Row%20in%20Qatar%20NOW.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKaypius%20is%20the%20pen%20name%20for%20the%20writer%2C%20a%20full-time%20aviator.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20realkaypius%40gmail.com%20and%20tweets%20at%20%40realkaypius.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%20the%20writer%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkaypius.com%2F2023%2F10%2F27%2Fa-coursemates-plea-to-bring-back-naval-veterans-on-death-row-in-qatar-now%2F%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698415200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F27184644%2Fmodi-thani.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fcoursemate-appeal-indian-navy-veterans-death-row-qatar%22%